-list-label-0\" class=\"abl-inline\"><span>Tags:&nbsp;</span></p><ul class=\"abl-inline abl-list-reset\" aria-labelledby=\"tags-list-label-0\"><li class=\"abl-inline\"><a\n                  href=\"/es/blog/tags/ableton-product/live-12/\"\n                  rel=\"tag\"\n                ><span>Live 12</span><span class=\"visually-hidden\"> – View posts with tag: Live 12</span></a><span aria-hidden=\"true\">,&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"abl-inline\"><a\n                  href=\"/es/blog/tags/ableton-features/expressive-chords/\"\n                  rel=\"tag\"\n                ><span>Expressive Chords</span><span class=\"visually-hidden\"> – View posts with tag: Expressive Chords</span></a><span aria-hidden=\"true\">,&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"abl-inline\"><a\n                  href=\"/es/blog/tags/ableton-features/stem-separation/\"\n                  rel=\"tag\"\n                ><span>Stem Separation</span><span class=\"visually-hidden\"> – View posts with tag: Stem Separation</span></a><span aria-hidden=\"true\">,&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"abl-inline\"><a\n                  href=\"/es/blog/tags/brands/splice/\"\n                  rel=\"tag\"\n                ><span>Splice</span><span class=\"visually-hidden\"> – View posts with tag: Splice</span></a><span aria-hidden=\"true\">,&nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"abl-inline\"><a\n                  href=\"/es/blog/tags/ableton-features/auto-pan-tremolo/\"\n                  rel=\"tag\"\n                ><span>Auto Pan-Tremolo</span><span class=\"visually-hidden\"> – View posts with tag: Auto Pan-Tremolo</span></a></li></ul></div></header><div class=\"blog-entry__content\"><div class=\"content has-full-width-images abl-mt-0\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--content text-container\" id=\"texto-245037\"><p>Check out the new features in the upcoming Live 12.3 update in this overview video by Seed to Stage. See how he lays down drums for a remix using Stem Separation, finds the right loops to layer on top with Splice – 