 class=\"main-nav__slideable\"><ul class=\"main-nav__row main-nav__link-list\"><li class=\"main-nav__col main-nav__col--25p\"><a href=\"/es/blog/categories/loop/\"><div><h4>Loop</h4><p>Watch Talks, Performances and Features from Ableton\'s Summit for Music Makers</p></div></a></li><li class=\"main-nav__col main-nav__col--25p\"><a href=\"https://learningmusic.ableton.com/es/\"><div><h4>Learning Music</h4><p>Learn the fundamentals of music making right in your browser.</p></div></a></li><li class=\"main-nav__col main-nav__col--25p\"><a href=\"https://learningsynths.ableton.com/es/\"><div><h4>Learning Synths</h4><p>Get started with synthesis using a web-based synth and accompanying lessons.</p></div></a></li><li class=\"main-nav__col main-nav__col--25p\"><a href=\"https://makingmusic.ableton.com/\"><div><h4>Making Music</h4><p>Some tips from 74 Creative Strategies for Electronic Producers.</p></div></a></li></ul></div></div></section></div></div><div class=\"main-nav__stretcher\"></div></nav><div class=\"main-nav__separator\"></div><nav aria-label=\'secondary\'><ul class=\"main-nav__link-list main-nav__link-list--secondary\"><li class=\"main-nav__link-list__item is-active\"><a href=\"/es/community/user-groups/\" aria-current=\"page\">Find User Groups</a></li><li class=\"main-nav__link-list__item\"><a href=\"/community/user-groups/organizing-ableton-user-group/\" >Organize User Groups</a></li></ul></nav></header><div class=\"page\"><main><section class=\"panel\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--content text-container\" id=\"texto-199851\"><h2 dir=\"ltr\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-1980507c-7fff-ccae-a8a8-b414b89ec80d\">No existe una manera más enriquecedora de impulsar tu creatividad que intercambiando ideas y experiencias con personas afines en el ámbito musical. Independientemente de si estás dando tus primeros pasos o si ya cuentas con experiencia en el uso de diversas versiones de Ableton Live, en los User Groups encontrarás una comunidad diversa e inclusiva de músicos y productores. Estas personas comparten una pasión por la música y están dispuestas a intercambiar conocimientos y experiencias sobre Live y Push.</b></h2><h2></h2><h2 dir=\"ltr\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-1980507c-7fff-ccae-a8a8-b414b89ec80d\">Consulta la lista de Ableton User Groups en tu país para localizar el más próximo a ti. Únete a esta comunidad vibrante y diversa para potenciar tu creatividad musical y aprender de forma colaborativa</b></h2></div></section><div class=\"packs-wrapper loading\" ng-app=\"abl.filter\" ng-controller=\"Filter\" loaded=\"loaded\"><div class=\"filters\"><div class=\"filters__categories\"><div class=\"filters__categories__item\" ng-click=\"set_item_type(\'all\')\" ng-class=\"{active:item_type===\'all\'}\"></div></div><div class=\"filters__localization\"><div class=\"filters__localization__dropdown icon-arrow\"><select ng-model=\"single_selected_by_category[\'country\']\" ng-change=\"single_selected_by_category_updated(\'country\')\" ng-options=\"tag as trans(tag) for tag in tags[\'country\'] | orderBy:trans | filter:tag_is_visible(\'country\')\"><option value=\"\">All countries</option></select></div></div><header class=\"filters__header\"><div class=\"filters__header__title\" trainer-title=\"trainer-title\"></div><div class=\"filters__header__reset-filters\" ng-click=\"clear_filtering()\" ng-show=\"is_filtering_applied()\">Mostrar todo</div></header></div><div class=\"four-up with-padding with-equal-height\"><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"301\" ng-show=\"items[301]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/community/amcj_2023_NVWgYSl.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Ableton and Max Community Japan (AMCJ)</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>AMCJは音楽や音をプログラム開発の次元から掘り下げるサウンドハッカーのためのワークショップイベントを毎月東京&amp;オンラインで開催中。</p><p>ジャンルや背景、習熟度や制作環境、性別、国籍を問わず、様々な価値観を持つ全てのクリエイターの学びを応援します。</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Akiyuki Okayasu\n                \n              </p><p>\n                \n                  Kentaro Suzuki\n                \n              </p><p><a href=\"mailto:info@akihikomatsumoto.com\">Akihiko Matsumoto</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/AMCJ_Official\" class=\"has-arrow\">X (Twitter)</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"131\" ng-show=\"items[131]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/ableton_tokyo_meet-up.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Ableton Meetup Tokyo</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Ableton Meetup Tokyo is Tokyo-based Ableton user community which aims to make a sustainable musical life for all musicians.</p><p>We use Ableton Live, the Berlin-born music production software, and participate in various events from conferences to outdoor parties in order&nbsp;to make a place to exchange ideas with the keyword &ldquo;meetup&rdquo;.</p><p>Also, we have regular meetup events to discuss and present our own usage of Ableton Live, each time we invite artists, DJ and engineers to hear their stories.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/yoshitaka-koyasu/#?item_type=all&amp;country=country_jp\">Yoshitaka Koyasu</a></p><p>\n                \n                  Akihiko Satoda\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://ableton-meetup.tokyo/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Website</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AbletonMeetupTokyo/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/AMT_TYO\" class=\"has-arrow\">Twitter</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/abletonmeetuptokyo/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Instagram</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"166\" ng-show=\"items[166]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/almada_lisboa_ug_fb_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Almada - Lisbon</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>O Ableton Users Group ~ Lisboa &eacute; uma iniciativa que convida todos os utilizadores do Ableton Live, principiantes ou profissionais, residentes ou visitantes, &agrave; reuni&atilde;o para a partilha de ideias, t&eacute;cnicas de produ&ccedil;&atilde;o ou ferramentas &uacute;teis &agrave; utiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o do Live, tudo no sentido de melhorar o workflow e aperfei&ccedil;oar o dom&iacute;nio sobre o programa.&nbsp;<br />\r\nJ&aacute; que a utiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o deste consiste numa experi&ecirc;ncia mais individualista, convidamos &agrave; aproxima&ccedil;&atilde;o de todos para que as nossas ideias nos influenciem uns aos outros e, com isso, a nossa experi&ecirc;ncia com o Live se torne mais rica e completa!&nbsp;<br />\r\nTodos s&atilde;o bem-vindos, pois acreditamos que a chave se encontra na partilha de pequenas ou grandes ideias que, no final, fazem toda a diferen&ccedil;a.<br /><br />\r\nConvidamo-vos, ent&atilde;o, a juntarem-se a n&oacute;s nas reuni&otilde;es, que surgir&atilde;o no Desterro, de forma regular, em datas a anunciar. Tragam as vossas t&eacute;cnicas de produ&ccedil;&atilde;o pr&oacute;prias, os pequenos segredos do Live que quiserem partilhar nestas reuni&otilde;es, o vosso gear, enfim, tudo aquilo que acharem que melhora a vossa experi&ecirc;ncia com o Live.&nbsp;<br />\r\nPartilhar &eacute; aprender.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Tiago Tryambaka\n                \n              </p><p>\n                \n                  Carolina Silva\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/103533576806522/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"153\" ng-show=\"items[153]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/f7/09/f7096b16-6f30-47b2-a4fa-f8497d6a2441/amsterdam_ug_fb_banner_1.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Amsterdam</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>The Ableton User Group Amsterdam helps users of Ableton Live, Max for Live and Ableton Push to share their ideas, host workshops and offer a platform to meet other users.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Camiel Daamen\n                \n              </p><p>\n                \n                  Arwen Kelly\n                \n              </p><p>\n                \n                  Nikesh Katwa\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/405964036262163/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"180\" ng-show=\"items[180]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/andalucia_3ybouOW.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Andalucia</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Grupo dedicado a Ableton live, max for live y todas las dudas que tengamos, tambi&eacute;n compartid vuestra m&uacute;sica y enlaces a vuestros proyecto para difundir.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Jose Luis Callejón Pedrosa\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/183800011780702/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"55\" ng-show=\"items[55]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/annecy_ug_fb_banner1.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Annecy</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Bienvenue sur le Annecy Ableton User Group (AAUG) !</p><p>Ce groupe est ouvert &agrave; tous, que vous soyez d&eacute;j&agrave; utilisateur averti d&#39;Ableton, instrumentiste/chanteur, ou simplement curieux de d&eacute;couvrir le monde de la M.A.O. Vous aurez ainsi l&#39;opportunit&eacute;:</p><p>&bull; d&#39;&eacute;changer autour de la musique</p><p>&bull; de rencontrer des artistes locaux</p><p>&bull; de partager votre exp&eacute;rience</p><p>&bull; de vous mettre en relation avec les diff&eacute;rents acteurs du paysage musical (compositeurs/interpr&egrave;tes, ing&eacute;nieurs du son, salles de spectacles...)</p><p>Ce groupe est aussi le votre, donc si vous avez des bons plans, des d&eacute;couvertes ou des &eacute;v&egrave;nements locaux, n&#39;h&eacute;sitez pas &agrave; les partager.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  François Decourcelle\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/annecyabletonusergroup\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"94\" ng-show=\"items[94]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/01/3e/013e0be5-b7a7-4235-bfc0-7b5354289020/athens_user_group_fb_banner_2.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Athens</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Whether you are producing, performing with Ableton Live, or you are just a person with passion for music and want to learn more about it, you are welcome to this page!</p><p>We are hosting events with discussions, workshops and artist demonstrations on Ableton Live and Max For Live.</p><p>You don\'t have to be a rocket scientist to join us, neither are we! If you enjoy Ableton Live and the process of learning, sharing and working together, \'Like\' our page to join us and get informed about upcoming meetups!</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Kostas Georgiou\n                \n              </p><p>\n                \n                  Mike Kyriallidis\n                \n              </p><p>\n                \n                  Stavros Foskolos\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"mailto:athens.ableton.live.user.group@gmail.com\" class=\"has-arrow\">athens.ableton.live.user.group@gmail.com</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1791690607617430/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"230\" ng-show=\"items[230]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/atlanta_ug_fb_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Atlanta</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>One of the longest running User Groups in the United States since 2007. We are Atlanta, GA area producers, DJs, and electronic musicians from all walks of life, spanning many genres. The Atlanta Ableton User Group is all about sharing knowledge and a good place to make connections with other Live users. We have monthly events involving workshops, jam sessions, and live performances located throughout the metro Atlanta area. Please visit the Atlanta Ableton UG on Facebook to join and stay informed.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  John Jacobus\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AbletonATL\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"231\" ng-show=\"items[231]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/austin_ug_fb_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Austin</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>We are a group of people in the Austin area that use Ableton live. We are producers, D.J.&#39;s, and electronic musicians from many walks of life, spanning many genres. Check the calender for workshops, performances, and events around town. Feel free to come by an event. Send us a message if you would like to join the group, learn about live, or if you would like to host an event.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/tom-carlile/#?item_type=all&amp;country=country_united-states\">Tom Carlile</a></p><p>\n                \n                  Edgar Uribe\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/abletonATX/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"103\" ng-show=\"items[103]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/bali_ug_fb.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Bali</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p><i data-stringify-type=\"italic\">With its varied landscape of hills and mountains, rugged coastlines and sandy beaches, lush rice terraces and barren volcanic hillsides </i><i data-stringify-type=\"italic\">all providing a picturesque backdrop to its colourful, deeply spiritual and unique culture, Bali stakes a serious claim to be paradise on earth. </i><i data-stringify-type=\"italic\">Bali is renowned for its diverse and sophisticated art forms, enchants with its dramatic dances and colorful ceremonies, its arts, and crafts, </i><i data-stringify-type=\"italic\">to its world class surfing spots and exciting nightlife.</i><br/><br/><i data-stringify-type=\"italic\">Bali, source of inspiration, fuel of creativity, gathers passionate independent Artists ready to share their knowledge and experience </i><i data-stringify-type=\"italic\">with brand new Ableton Live users or experienced Max Patch developpers through monthly Events based on Masterclasses, Talks and Q&amp;R .</i></p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Guillaume Ravenel\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/baliabletonusergroup\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"181\" ng-show=\"items[181]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/barcelona_ug_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Barcelona</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Grupo creado con la intenci&oacute;n de ser un punto de encuentro para compartir conocimientos, trucos e ideas, adem&aacute;s de resolver dudas sobre Ableton Live. Tambi&eacute;n organizamos workshops gratuitos de Ableton Live en Barcelona.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Albert Domenech\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/288367407848801/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"110\" ng-show=\"items[110]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/aug_bari.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Bari</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Ableton User Group Bari nasce con l\'obiettivo di far interagire e collaborare musicisti producer tra di loro, attraverso talk online ed offline. Inoltre organizzare jam session e sessioni in studi di registrazione, incontri con artisti locali e non solo.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Vito Loperfido\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/bariabletonusergroup\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"33\" ng-show=\"items[33]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/34/7e/347e6794-391e-4c38-83b7-1360bd3ba41d/beijing_ableton_user_group_fb_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Beijing</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p style=\"\">We&rsquo;re aiming to build an open communication platform for Ableton Live users in Beijing. Whether you&rsquo;re a professional music producer, or a music lover who is getting started with Ableton Live, this is a group for all levels of users. If you have the passion to learn, share and build connections with other producers and artists, we welcome you to join this user group. We want to encourage and assist Ableton Live users in Beijing, and build an active music community in the city.</p><p style=\"\">To join the WeChat group please email your WeChat ID to&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:peiyuchen1998@qq.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">peiyuchen1998@qq.com<sup><img align=\"absmiddle\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" height=\"12\" src=\"https://jira.ableton.com/images/icons/mail_small.gif\" width=\"13\" /></sup></a></p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/peiyu-chen/\">Peiyu Chen</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"138\" ng-show=\"items[138]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/lebanon_ug_fb_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Beirut</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p class=\"meta\">A community in which new and old members join forces, get to know each other, share news, discuss ideas, plan, and collaborate.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Mohamad Ghebris\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/AbletonLebanon/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"75\" ng-show=\"items[75]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/berlin_ug_fb_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Berlin</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>The Ableton User Group Berlin is for all interested Ableton Live users based in (or visiting) Berlin. All levels are welcome. The meetings are in both German and English.</p><p>The aim of the Group is to help Live users network and share information and experience in an informal environment with each other. The meetings are to allow all participants to suggest discussion themes related to Ableton Live, as well as to provide a forum for presenting their own work.</p><p>We also have artist&nbsp;meetings and expert talks which aim to give an insight into how Ableton Live is used in different production and performance contexts, providing insider&nbsp;tips for optimizing workflows. User Group participants are encouraged to present their own work at the meetings with a live or DJ set at the end of the meetings. All Ableton Live users are invited to provide ideas and suggestions for discussions.</p><p>The meetups take place monthly at <a href=\"http://www.pankecultu­re.com/\">Panke</a> in Berlin-Wedding, Gerichtstra&szlig;e 23, 2nd Building (2.HH). For actual dates please visit our FB Page or Meetup.com page:</p><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/739401529446226/\">Ableton User Group Berlin on Facebook</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/abletonusergroupberlin\">Ableton User Group Berlin Page (also accessible to non-Facebook users)</a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Berlin-Ableton-User-Group\">Ableton User Group on Meetup</a></p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/de/certified-training/brian-smith/#?item_type=all&amp;country=country_germany\">Brian Smith</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/maya-consuelo-sternel/#?item_type=all&amp;country=country_germany\">Maya Consuelo Sternel</a></p><p><a href=\"https://linktr.ee/evavandijk\">Eva van Dijk</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/739401529446226/about/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/abletonusergroupberlin/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Instagram</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"196\" ng-show=\"items[196]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/c5/53/c5531e01-f3d3-4918-b4bb-47fe58fe39bb/bern_ableton_user_group_logo.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Bern</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Die offizielle Ableton User Group in Bern zum Austausch von Ideen und Gedanken rund um Ableton Live. Sie steht Ableton Usern auf jedem Level offen. Strictly no self promotion! Es finden Treffen zu verschiedensten Themen wie MaxMSP, Live Performance, News, Synths, Technologien, Composing etc. statt.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/emanuel-frey/#?item_type=all&amp;country=country_switzerland\">Emanuel Frey</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/abletonbern\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"132\" ng-show=\"items[132]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/da/bf/dabfc34f-26d1-40de-bea4-85b679b6ee51/bigakko_1969_ug_fb_banner3.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Bigakko 1969</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>美学校は1969年に開講したインディペンデントな表現のための学びの場です。</p><p>音楽のみならず絵画やアート、映像、演劇など、様々な表現や人々に開かれてきたこの空間をすべてのAbleton Liveユーザーに開放します。</p><p>開放日は毎月第2日曜。Ableton Liveユーザーのための交流・制作会として、ジャンルやシーンを超えたティップスや意見交換の場として機能していきます。各方面よりトラックメーカーなどを招いてのレクチャーなども予定しています。</p><p>あらゆる音楽家の創造性にとって開かれた場となりますことを。</p><p>&nbsp;</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Yuichi Nagao\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/ableton.user.group.bigakko.1969/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"182\" ng-show=\"items[182]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/bilbao_ableton_ug_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Bilbao</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Ableton User Group Bilbao es un foro de encuentro para los amantes de la creaci&oacute;n musical en genera</p><ul></ul></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Fernando Carvalho\n                \n              </p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"56\" ng-show=\"items[56]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/bordeaux_ug.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Bordeaux</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Bonjour &agrave; tous et bienvenue sur le User Group Ableton Live Bordeaux.</p><p>► Ce groupe est public, vous pouvez donc inviter vos amis &agrave; le rejoindre.&nbsp;</p><p>► Dans ce groupe, vous pouvez poster tout ce qui est en rapport avec Ableton Live ou Max for Live, et la MAO - Nouveaut&eacute;s, techniques, d&eacute;bats, questions, id&eacute;es, etc.</p><p>► Nous nous r&eacute;unissons r&eacute;guli&egrave;rement dans des lieux divers et atypiques avec des Artistes, des &eacute;ducateurs et des professionnels d&eacute;sireux de partager leurs connaissances et leur exp&eacute;rience.&nbsp;</p><p>C&#39;est l&#39;occasion de rencontrer d&#39;autres utilisateurs de Live et de partager ensemble nos connaissances autour de divers &eacute;v&eacute;nements : Journ&eacute;e de pr&eacute;sentation, MasterClass, Concerts et Live, Jam-Session etc...&nbsp;</p><p>Merci et &agrave; bient&ocirc;t !</p><p>&nbsp;</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"mailto:mucadesign@hotmail.fr\">Müca Özer</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1754548311467914/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"234\" ng-show=\"items[234]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/boston_ug_fb_3.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Boston</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>We are the Boston, MA User Group. We are area producers, DJs, and electronic musicians from all walks of life, spanning many genres. Ableton Live is at the forefront of our production and performance techniques. This Ableton User Group is all about sharing knowledge and a good place to make connections. We have monthly events involving workshops, jam sessions, and live performances.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"mailto:tak.yamashi@gmail.com\">Tak Yamashi</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AbletonLiveUserGroupBoston\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"17\" ng-show=\"items[17]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/unsorted-uploads/brabant_wallon_ug_fb_banner2.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Brabant Wallon</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>We are a group whose vocation is to share the pleasure of making music with Ableton.&nbsp; And to do this, we exchange via this page and we meet regularly to make us discover our new creations, to seek together solutions to problems encountered, and to learn from each other&#39;s experiences.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We do not only accept Ableton Experts.&nbsp; Everyone is welcome, no matter if you are at the beginning of your journey or if the lands of computer-assisted music is a well known territory. But pay attention to the fact that we are a group most composed of French speaking people, so most of the exchanges are in French. So if this is ok for you, welcome to our family.&nbsp;</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Pierrot Legrain\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/brabantwallonabletonusergroup/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"57\" ng-show=\"items[57]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/97/47/9747efce-0c33-4c1d-b307-a867aee772e4/bretagne_ug_fb_banner_6.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Bretagne</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Bonjour &agrave; tous,</p><p>Nous sommes heureux de vous accueillir dans l&#39;Ableton User Group Bretagne !</p><p>Cr&eacute;&eacute; en 2009, le groupe a pour but d&#39;avoir une communaut&eacute; active d&#39;utilisateurs autour du logiciel Ableton Live. Que vous soyez fin connaisseur, d&eacute;butant, amateur confirm&eacute; ou tout simplement int&eacute;ress&eacute;, ce groupe est gratuit et ouvert &agrave; tous ! Cela vous offre l&#39;opportunit&eacute; de vous perfectionner et d&#39;&eacute;tendre vos connaissances dans le domaine de la musique assist&eacute;e par ordinateur (M.A.O).</p><p>Nous privil&eacute;gions l&#39;&eacute;change, le partage et le transfert de connaissances, et tout cela est permis gr&acirc;ce &agrave; votre investissement au sein de cette communaut&eacute;.</p><p>Retrouvez-nous sur notre groupe Facebook, afin de partager connaissances, tutoriels et p&eacute;dagogies, directement sur la page, au cours de Livestreams ou lors de rencontres r&eacute;elles.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/vincent-le-bartz/#?item_type=all&amp;country=country_france\">Vincent Le Bartz</a></p><p>\n                \n                  Victorien Bourreau\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/186171134405/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p><p><a href=\"mailto:AbletonGroupBretagne@icloud.com\" class=\"has-arrow\">Email</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"211\" ng-show=\"items[211]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/55/25/5525148c-9fee-4d78-9b3a-3ef10b027005/brighton_ug_banner.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Brighton</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>The Ableton User Group Brighton is for all those interested in Ableton Live based in and around Brighton and Hove. All levels are welcome.</p><p>We are passionate about developing a strong electronic music scene in Brighton.</p><p>We will be hosting meet ups that give Ableton users a chance to perform, develop and network in the city of Brighton.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Elliot Turnley\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/abletonusergroupbrighton/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Instagram</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/376609772695783/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"3\" ng-show=\"items[3]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/brisbane_ug_fb_banner1.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Brisbane</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>We are a community group for Creators, Producers, Performers &amp; DJ\'s with Ableton at the heart of their project. Our mission is to help develop the local music community through enabling members to share their ideas, techniques and creations.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Jarrod Bartlett\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/AbletonLiveUserGroupBrisbane\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"212\" ng-show=\"items[212]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/bristol_ug_fb_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Bristol</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>A dedicated area/group now available for all discussions,debates,tips,and tunes associated within the marvel that is Ableton.</p><p>This can also be a place to exchange Max4live ideas,plugins and builds for the more experienced user,however it is not solely for experienced Live users but to be used to solve any basic or mid level problems you may have within Ableton. This group is run by Elevator Sound Bristol</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"mailto:james@elevatorsound.com\">James Waterworth &amp; Elevator Sound Bristol</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"http://elevatorsound.com/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Elevator Sound Bristol</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1522357848023659/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"236\" ng-show=\"items[236]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/brooklyn_ug_fb_banner2.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Brooklyn</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>The Brooklyn Ableton User Group aims to support and foster the local music-maker community in Brooklyn New York.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Dave Garnish\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/292993903044296\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"299\" ng-show=\"items[299]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/bruges_ableton_ug.jpeg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Bruges</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Ableton User Group Bruges is een community van en voor Ableton gebruikers.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Hanne Vantuyne\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/abletonusergroupbruges\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p><p><a href=\"discord.gg/aDDKfpZETn\" class=\"has-arrow\">Discord</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"16\" ng-show=\"items[16]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placehold