iption\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>This is the Changsha Ableton User Group. Whether you&#39;re an expert, a newbie, or somewhere in between, the most important thing is that you enjoy using Ableton Live and are willing to learn, share, and collaborate. We welcome everyone who loves music production to join us for free meet-ups and open discussions. You can send us an email and we will invite you to the official WeChat discussion group.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  琛琛\n                \n              </p><p>\n                \n                  Min9\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"mailto:chenliumusic@163.com\" class=\"has-arrow\">chenliumusic@163.com</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"77\" ng-show=\"items[77]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/chemnitz_new_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Chemnitz</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"\">Cross-genre and open to all, Musikkombinat&nbsp;Chemnitz&nbsp;offers a versatile platform.</p><p>Workshops, meetups and listening sessions as well as lectures on music production take place here once a month.</p><p>Exchange in the community and regular updates as well as more details can be found in the event details, in the AUG&nbsp;Chemnitz&nbsp;group and on the various social media channels.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Falko Kraus\n                \n              </p><p>\n                \n                  Jonas Körner\n                \n              <