iv></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"239\" ng-show=\"items[239]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/59/42/594240db-b8d5-4d50-8310-9925986448ee/cleveland_ug_fb_banner2.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Cleveland</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>The Cleveland Ableton User Group is hosted by Ableton Certified Trainer Ricky Graham as part of the Cleveland Art, Music and Technology Meet-Up.</p><p>All musicians, producers, technologists, visual artists, creatives, composers, coders, and makers welcome! <br/><br/>\nMeet, grab a coffee, share your art/wares. Talks and presentations will be scheduled prior to each meeting. A venue will be announced in advance of each meeting.</p><p></p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/ricky-graham/\">Ricky Graham</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/clevelandabletonusergroup/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/artmusictech/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Meetup</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"42\" ng-show=\"items[42]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/unsorted-uploads/colombia.jpeg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Colombia</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Ableton Live User Group Colombia es una comunidad de usuarios locales de este fant&aacute;stico software donde podemos crecer y enriquecernos mutuamente compartiendo conocimiento sobre sus usos y funciones.</p><p>Para esto usaremos esta p&aacute;gina como plataforma de comunicaci&oacute;n principal y tambi&eacute;n haremos reuniones y eventos peri&oacute;dicos donde est&aacute;ran invitados a asistir y a participar. No importa si sabes mucho o sabes poco, no importa donde o como estudies, no importa cuantos a&ntilde;os tienes, no importa que musica quieras hacer, este espacio es de TODOS y para TODOS! Bienvenidos</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/david-najera/#?item_type=all&amp;country=country_colombia\">David Najera</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pages/Ableton-Live-User-Group-Colombia/372066826285436\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"241\" ng-show=\"items[241]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/columbus_ug_fb_banner1.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Columbus</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>This Ableton User Group is for all interested Ableton Live users based in or visiting Columbus, Ohio. The aim of this group is to create a user network for sharing information, and to share experience and resources with each other. Meet-ups contain: speaker presenting lightning talks on a variety of Ableton-oriented topics and their working processes, open time for live collaboration, guest artist sessions, and more. Everyone is welcome!</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Brandon Zeeb\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/ColumbusOhioAbletonUserGroup/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"47\" ng-show=\"items[47]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/copenhagen_ug_fb_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Copenhagen</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">A motley collective of producers, musicians,&nbsp;listeners,&nbsp;g33ks, and other good people. Together we seek to facilitate the fun in collaboration and creation // This by meeting likeminded people out in the real world. We do workshops, seminars, show-off sessions, g33k-mingling, speed dating, concerts, and much, much more.<br />\r\nBe welcome in ALUGC - Ableton Live User Group Copenhagen - we&#39;re cooler than our acronym!</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/rasmus-kjaerbo/\">Rasmus Kjaerbo</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/abletonliveusergroupcopenhagen/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"43\" ng-show=\"items[43]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/unsorted-uploads/screenshot_2023-03-16_at_162305.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Costa Rica</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Ableton Live User Group Costa Rica es una Comunidad de Productores, Live Performers, M&uacute;sicos, DJs y Artistas interesados en ir m&aacute;s lejos con Ableton Live. Nos reunimos para explorar nuevas t&eacute;cnicas y herramientas con instructores y artistas invitados, plasmar nuestras ideas en proyectos y hacer m&uacute;sica.</p><p>En DJLAB utilizamos Ableton Live como Plataforma Creativa que contribuye al desarrollo de la creciente Comunidad local y regional.&nbsp;</p><p>Live Users de todos los Niveles son bienvenidos.&nbsp;</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Esteban Howell\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/608324175930327/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"44\" ng-show=\"items[44]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/unsorted-uploads/croatia.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Croatia</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Hrvatska Ableton grupa za razmjenu znanja, trikova i svega povezanog sa ovim kreativnim glazbenim softverom.&nbsp;<br />\r\nPriključite se i pozovite zainteresirane!</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Emil Herceg\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AbletonCroatiaUserGroup\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p><p><a href=\"mailto:emil@sonarscope.hr\" class=\"has-arrow\">emil@sonarscope.hr</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"243\" ng-show=\"items[243]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/75/89/7589f1a3-43ce-46bf-8d00-e3700292a426/daytona_ug_banner_2.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Daytona</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>The Daytona Ableton User Group is organised by Brad Moody. The meetings are held in English, for Ableton Live users based in or visiting Daytona Beach.&nbsp;<br /><br />\r\nWe organize events with local talent, Ableton specialists and trainers. Whether you are an Ableton Live expert, novice or somewhere in between; all users of all levels are welcome to join us and learn from each other, share, collaborate and exchange ideas.&nbsp;<br /><br />\r\nJoin us for artist demonstrations, expert talks and open discussions.<br />\r\nParticipants are also welcomed and encouraged to share their own work at the end of specific sessions.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Brad Moody\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/719412858459968/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"244\" ng-show=\"items[244]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/denver_ug_fb_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Denver</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>The Denver Ableton User Group is a community of Ableton users who meet monthly in Denver, CO in order to actively network and share knowledge.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/darren-kramer/\">Darren Kramer</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/denverabletonusergroup/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"215\" ng-show=\"items[215]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/edinburgh_ug_fb_banner4.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Edinburgh</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>We hope to bring like-minded people in the area together and create new relationships through Ableton Live. One of our main aims is to encourage&nbsp;the younger generation to try out new music technology.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Craig Penman\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/CEPF8vgsR9?fbclid=IwAR2Qjh7BWoXHX9wchlOopqjnwIDvuRJzPGM4Flq3CLZ0t4dA6t9v1lOEjEA\" class=\"has-arrow\">Discord</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/edinburghabletonusergroup/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"143\" ng-show=\"items[143]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/estado_de_mexico_ug_fb_banner1.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Estado de Mexico</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>User Group Estado de México es una comunidad de Productores, DJs y Artistas Usuarios de Ableton Live, que busca fomentar la participación, creatividad y aprendizaje a través de eventos en vivo y online que nos hagan crecer en conjunto mientras nos conectamos unos con otros.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Arturo Amador Martinez\n                \n              </p><p>\n                \n                  Luis &quot;LEAR&quot; Arcega \n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1177616239412153\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"302\" ng-show=\"items[302]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/usergroup-banner-image/4-black_text_export_file.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">FINTA+ Ableton User Group Switzerland</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>The FINTA+ Ableton User Group Switzerland has the goal to create a safer space for FINTA+ to share music production tips and tricks as well as empowering each other and create a constructive network. All levels are welcome and we adjust the language to the participants. It is a space where the participants can share information and experience in an informal environment and allows to suggest discussion themes as well as to provide a forum for presenting everyones one work.&nbsp;</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"mailto:contact@cegiu.com\">Cégiu</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/fintaabletonusergroupswitzerland\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"80\" ng-show=\"items[80]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/3b/87/3b870772-a9db-403f-8fdc-5b0fe2cdee14/frankfurt_ug_fb_banner_new_4.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Frankfurt</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Die Ableton User Group Frankfurt ist f&uuml;r alle interessierten Ableton Live User aus Frankfurt am Main (oder gerade&nbsp;zu Besuch in der Stadt). Willkommen sind alle User, ob Anf&auml;nger oder Profi. Es ist auch egal in welchem Genre du unterwegs bist. Die Usergroup soll das Netzwerken, den Austausch und das gemeinsame Lernen aller an Musik Interessierter f&ouml;rdern.&nbsp;</p><p>Die Treffen finden regelm&auml;ssig mit verschiedenen Themen und Experten statt. Es k&ouml;nnen bei den Treffen nat&uuml;rlich auch eigene Produktionen vorgestellt werden.</p><p>Die Kommunikation wird ebenso auf deutsch wie auf englisch gef&uuml;hrt.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Peter Hoeld\n                \n              </p><p>\n                \n                  Lukas Nitsch\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/198956293508751/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"81\" ng-show=\"items[81]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/screenshot_2023-08-02_at_102227.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Freiburg</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Die Ableton User Group Freiburg trifft sich ca.&nbsp;alle 1-2&nbsp;Monate und es sind alle angesprochen, die mit Ableton Live arbeiten oder daran interessiert sind, egal ob Anf&auml;nger oder Fortgeschrittene.</p><p>In der Usergroup Freiburg geht es um den Erfahrungsaustausch, Tipps, Tricks, Netzwerken, Fachsimpeln &amp; sampeln und was sonst noch so alles dazu geh&ouml;rt.</p><p>Die Termine werden per E-mail &amp; &uuml;ber die Facebookseite bekannt gegeben. Wer in den Verteiler aufgenommen werden m&ouml;chte schickt bitte eine mail an die unten angegebene Kontaktadresse. Bitte meldet Euch immer vorher an.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"mailto:ableton.freiburg@gmail.com\">Tim Charlemagne</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/abletonuserfreiburg\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"59\" ng-show=\"items[59]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/french_riviera_ug.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">French Riviera</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Ableton Live User Group in the French Riviera</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Bruce Lane\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/766074168865979\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"184\" ng-show=\"items[184]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/galicia_aug.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Galicia</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>This group is a project arising from the idea of teaching different ways of making music with Ableton Live.</p><p>The objective is to get together with people to learn and share, exchange experiences between users, perfect skills in production, making demonstrations and clarifying doubts on the software.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Alejandro Pardo Vazquez\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/AbletonLiveUserGalicia\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"216\" ng-show=\"items[216]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/8a/b8/8ab8bb93-d328-4b49-864d-9e036f2cc60d/glasgow_ug_banner_2.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Glasgow</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Glasgow is a city rich in musical talent and has seen electronic music artists, record labels and institutions such as Hudson Mohawke, Soma Records and Sub Club emerge over the past 3 decades. Our aim is to continue this by sharing knowledge with the future generation and empowering like-minded Ableton users. The Glasgow Ableton User Group takes place at Shoogle Studios.  Please join our Facebook group for details of our upcoming meet-ups and get involved with an incredible community of like-minded people.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/simon-stokes/\">Simon Stokes</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/150176391817646/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"185\" ng-show=\"items[185]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/granada_aug.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Granada</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Este es un grupo de la comunidad administrado por usuarios y no administrado oficialmente por Ableton AG</p><p>Grupo de Usuarios de Ableton de Granada creado para resolver dudas, compartir experiencias conocimientos y actividades.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Javier Melgard\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/338830646607115\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"36\" ng-show=\"items[36]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/guangxi_ug_fb_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Guangxi</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Welcome to the Guangxi Ableton User Group.</p><p>This group aims to build an open communication platform for Ableton Live users who live&nbsp;in the Guangxi area&nbsp;for the purposes of learning, sharing and creative cooperation.&nbsp;Whether you are a professional music producer or a beginner who is interested in electronic music production, we sincerely welcome you to join.</p><p><br />\r\nWe will continuously share learning materials as well as&nbsp;hold online and offline workshops to share the latest production skills and official information with everyone.<br />\r\nIf you are interested in joining our Guangxi User Group, please send your WeChat ID to the following email: 27644307@qq.com</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/wan/\">赵万 Wan</a></p><p>\n                \n                  Photo by ZuRong Li\n                \n              </p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"305\" ng-show=\"items[305]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/guangzhou_ug_fb_banner1_h3S8H3P.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Guangzhou</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>The Guangzhou Ableton User Group provides a localized and open communication platform for Live users of all levels. Whether you are a professional musician or an amateur, you are welcome in our group to share knowledge, exchange ideas or establish a cooperative relationship. We aim to learn and grow our knowledge of Ableton Live, Max for Live, or any sound creation method. We are happy to provide relevant support and build an active localized music community.</p><p>To join the WeChat group please email your WeChat ID to: <a href=\"http://fredmamono@gmail.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">fredmamono@gmail.com</a></p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://mafmadmaf.com/\">maf (mafmadmaf)</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"26\" ng-show=\"items[26]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/43/d0/43d021ac-9924-4828-a8e0-4ff7a7555ae5/halifax_ug_fb_banner_1.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Halifax</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>The Ableton User Group Halifax is for all interested Ableton Live users based in The Maritimes.<br/>\nEvents will be held in Halifax on a monthly basis. Online events will be held regularly.<br/>\nAll levels are welcome.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Angus Maclean\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/558319654826350/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"83\" ng-show=\"items[83]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/screenshot_2023-08-02_at_102434.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Hamburg</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"white-space: normal;\"><i>Die seit 2009 bestehende &ldquo;ABLETON USER GROUP HAMBURG&rdquo; ist ein offenes und kostenloses Treffen von EinsteigerInnen und Fortgeschrittenen, MusikerInnen, DJs und ProduzentInnen zum offenen Ideenaustausch. Sie bietet eine Plattform zum Gespr&auml;ch und zum Teilen von Erfahrungen. Egal ob Push, Live, Plugins, Controller oder auch Best Practice Workflow - Wer sehen und h&ouml;ren m&ouml;chte, wie andere musikbegeisterte Menschen mit &quot;LIVE&quot; arbeiten oder auch einfach ehrliches und konstruktives Feedback auf Augenh&ouml;he zum eigenen Material bekommen m&ouml;chte, ist hier genau richtig!<br />\r\nEs ist vollkommen egal, ob du Vollprofi mit den oberfettesten Referenzen oder Day1-EinsteigerIn im absoluten Greenhorn-Modus bist; du bist beim Event herzlich willkommen! Du bist aber auch herzlich eingeladen, wenn du einfach nur mal still gucken m&ouml;chtest.<br />\r\nUm eine Anmeldung &uuml;ber Eventbrite (zu finden bei der SAE) wird gebeten.</i></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"white-space: normal;\"><i>Wann und Wo:</i></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"white-space: normal;\"><i>An jedem zweiten Dienstag im Monat um 20 Uhr<br />\r\nSAE Institut Hamburg (Feldstrasse 66, 20359 HH)</i></span></span></span></p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"mailto:jan.spanier@gmail.com\">Jan F.J. Spanier</a></p><p><a href=\"mailto:post@ole-sieber.de\">Ole Sieber</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AbletonUserGroupHamburg\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/abletonusergrouphamburg/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Instagram</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"37\" ng-show=\"items[37]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/hangzhou_ug_fb_banner1.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Hangzhou</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>This is the Hangzhou Ableton User Group. Our purpose is to build a free and open communication platform for Ableton Live users. We welcome all musicians, artists, and sound engineers who are willing to share, including Ableton Live beginners and enthusiasts.<br />\r\nWe will share learning materials and production techniques from time to time, hold online and offline exchange meetings, and share the latest official Ableton information with everyone. We hope this place can become a place of inspiration for Hangzhou users to jointly improve technology and communicate ideas.<br />\r\nIf you want to join, you can add the organizer&#39;s WeChat account and send a personal introduction or purpose for joining the group.<br />\r\nWe will invite you to the official WeChat discussion group.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Guan (guanboyang002)\n                \n              </p><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/juny/#?item_type=all&amp;country=country_china\">Juny (kjqinyu1)</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"291\" ng-show=\"items[291]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/62/49/6249e24b-8714-4371-9bed-760c25d5789d/hcmc_ug_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Ho Chi Minh City</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>English:</p><p>We are the Ableton User Community in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam. This group is a place where the members can connect, share ideas and experiments, collaborate and learn new tricks. The community is open to all users, regardless of new or old, as long as you are willing to learn and ready to share.</p><p>Vietnamese:</p><p>Cộng đồng người dùng Phần mềm Ableton tại Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh, Việt Nam. Nơi kết nối để chia sẻ ý tưởng, thử nghiệm, cộng tác và học các thủ thuật mới. Cộng đồng mở cho tất cả người dùng, không phân biệt người mới hay cũ, chỉ cần bạn đã sẵn sàng học hỏi và sẵn sàng chia sẻ</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Thuy Linh Duong\n                \n              </p><p>\n                \n                  Nhat Minh Tran\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/645600389113335/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"96\" ng-show=\"items[96]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/03/cc/03ccb9af-4b52-4a4f-8e1a-f4fd82559566/hong_kong_ug_fb_banner2.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Hong Kong</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>The Ableton User Group Hong Kong is for all interested Ableton Live users based in (or visiting) Hong Kong. All levels are welcome.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Aaron Tsoi\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AbletonUserGroupHongKong/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"248\" ng-show=\"items[248]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/houston_ug.jpeg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Houston</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Want to Produce, DJ, create music, loops, stems, mangle audio beyond anything you could imagine? Then Ableton Live is for you. Join the Users Group to see what it&#39;s all about. If you are already a user, you can share your knowledge with others.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Russel Dunlap\n                \n              </p><p>\n                \n                  Ashish Tripathi\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pages/Houston-Ableton-Users-Group/142553442438179\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"250\" ng-show=\"items[250]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/cf/86/cf8689df-b43a-41fe-9389-b23349a05642/hudson_valley_user_group_banner_new.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Hudson Valley</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Like Electronic Music? This group is for EM enthusiasts and people who work with or want to learn Ableton Live, Synthesis and Electronic Music Production in the Hudson Valley. A place to post pix, meeting info, videos, tips &amp; tricks. </p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Neil Alexander\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/AbletonHVUG/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"108\" ng-show=\"items[108]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/israel_ug_fb_banner3.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Israel</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>The Israel User Group aims to build a supportive community of music makers in the Tel Aviv area. Live users of all levels are welcome to have a drink with us, share knowledge and learn from the best. If you\'d like to find out more about our group, please see our Facebook group or get in touch with Noam Sperber.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Noam Sperber\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/ableton/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"204\" ng-show=\"items[204]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/istanbul_aug.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Istanbul</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p><b>(ENG)</b></p><p>Ableton User Group Istanbul is a platform for everyone who wants to learn, share their knowledge, and be a part of a local community that is dedicated to Ableton Live and making electronic music. Every skill level -from beginner to expert- and interest in any genre is welcome. We curate workshops, live performances and exchange our works via our Facebook and Discord pages. Please feel free to get involved and enlarge our community for the better.</p><p><b>(TR)</b></p><p>Ableton User Group İstanbul; &ouml;ğrenmek, bildiklerini paylaşmak ve yerel bir kom&uuml;nitenin par&ccedil;ası olmak isteyen herkes i&ccedil;in Ableton Live ve elektronik m&uuml;zik &uuml;retimi odaklı bir platformdur. Her seviyeden ve her m&uuml;zik tarzıyla ilgilenen herkese a&ccedil;ık olup, ilgilenenleri buluşturma ve temasta tutmayı ama&ccedil;lar. Workshop&rsquo;lar, konserler d&uuml;zenliyor ve Facebook ve Discord sayfalarımız &uuml;zerinden işlerimizi birbirimizle paylaşıyoruz. Dileyen herkesi ağımızı genişletmeye ve g&uuml;zelleştirmeye bekliyoruz!</p><p>&nbsp;</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Akın Orbay\n                \n              </p><p>\n                \n                  Ahmetcan Gökçeer\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/abletonug.istanbul\" class=\"has-arrow\">Instagram</a></p><p><a href=\"abletonugistanbul@gmail.com\" class=\"has-arrow\">Email</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/ableton.istanbul/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p><p><a href=\"https://discord.gg/BcwUhebRKA\" class=\"has-arrow\">Discord</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"114\" ng-show=\"items[114]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/italia.jpeg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Italia</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Ableton Live User Group &egrave; un gruppo per gli utenti italiani di Ableton Live, gestito dal distributore italiano ufficiale (Backline) e dai Trainer Certificati Ableton. I trainer e i centri certificati presenteranno qui i corsi Ableton e cercheranno di rispondere a domande, dubbi e richieste.</p><p>The group meetings are held in Ableton Certified Training Centers.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Andrea Negrinelli\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/ableton.italy/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"205\" ng-show=\"items[205]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/kampala_ug_fb_banner1.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Kampala</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>The Kampala Ableton User Group\'s mission is to bring people together and tell the stories of Uganda through music.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Gabriel Mundaka\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/kampalaabletonusergroup/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"49\" ng-show=\"items[49]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/03/50/0350fb36-7fab-4891-8f85-677dc5fcf6d8/kitu_ableton_user_group_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Kitu</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Ableton User Group Kitu nace de la necesidad de crear una comunidad para todos los entusiastas y profesionales del audio que usan Ableton Live en el Ecuador, sin fines de lucro. Damos la bienvenida a cualquier persona que esté comprometida en crear una base sólida para todos, en la cual se pueda aprender, compartir y colaborar como iguales, con respeto y sin discriminación, mientras apoyamos la diversidad y la inclusividad.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/juan-fernando-cifuentes-moreta-k-diablo-kiteno/#?item_type=all&amp;country=country_ecuador\">Juan Fernando Cifuentes Moreta</a></p><p>\n                \n                  David Acosta\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/kituabletonusergroup/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"252\" ng-show=\"items[252]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/d8/f6/d8f6a9fe-a5cf-4a87-a5ca-2ae561961fea/75317257_962482377472145_5121829838570651648_o.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Knoxville</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>All are welcome here! If you are interested in learning more about Ableton Live, Push, Link or Max for Live this is the place for you. In this group you will find answers to your toughest questions, non-judgmental support and creative encouragement. This User Group will host workshops, shows and events that will help you bring your music productions to the next level. Users of all DAWS are welcome. Currently this group is moderated by Pellissippi State Community College Audio Engineering adjunct faculty Christina Horn. Miss Horn has developed the curriculum for Ableton users in the program and welcomes all ages, levels and styles.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Christina Horn\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/knoxvilleabletonusergroup/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"141\" ng-show=\"items[141]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/9e/5c/9e5c844b-0fc4-4f89-ba23-fe996eb23add/kuala_lumpur_ug_banner4.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Kuala Lumpur</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>The Kuala Lumpur Ableton User Group aims to form meaningful local connections between music enthusiasts and professionals of all ages through music/audio technology whilst encouraging learning, healthy discussions, sharing and collaboration.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Alicia Ngiam\n                \n              </p><p>\n                \n                  Reuben Samuel\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/151781495694461/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"206\" ng-show=\"items[206]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/kyiv_ug.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Kyiv</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>We are beginning, middle, and expert users of Ableton Live who live in Kyiv, Ukraine. The aim of this group is to help&nbsp;each other&nbsp;upgrade our knowledge of Ableton and music production in general, and to create a new level of Music Creation Philosophy in Ukraine - because we are a singing and musical nation. Sound is everywhere.&nbsp;</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Eugene Malishkevich\n                \n              </p><p>\n                \n                  Alexandr Dmytrenko\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/AbletonUKR\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"63\" ng-show=\"items[63]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/la_reunion_ug_fb_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">La Reunion</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Bienvenue au Ableton User Group - La R&eacute;union</p><p>► Une communaut&eacute; d&#39;artistes, producers, beatmakers, musiciens pro, ing&eacute;nieurs du son et/ou amateurs passionn&eacute;s. Nous nous r&eacute;unissons dans des lieux divers et atypiques afin de partager nos connaissances et notre exp&eacute;rience.</p><p>► Dans ce groupe, vous pouvez poster tout ce qui est en rapport avec Ableton Live ou Max for Live, et la MAO - Nouveaut&eacute;s, techniques, d&eacute;bats, questions, id&eacute;es, etc.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/remi-cazal/\">Remi Cazal</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/abletonusergrouplareunion/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"253\" ng-show=\"items[253]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/bd/fe/bdfebd70-2114-45b7-85e6-79dda3e6c5d0/las_vegas_ableton_user_group_fb_banner2.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Las Vegas</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Las Vegas Ableton User Group is a collection of Ableton producers and engineers of all skill levels. We will meet up several times a year to share ideas, knowledge, and works. New members welcome!</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  John Lloyd\n                \n              </p><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/antonio-sage/\">Antonio Sage</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/927373144108098/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Las-Vegas-Ableton-User-Group/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Meetup</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"115\" ng-show=\"items[115]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/a1/34/a1344779-31dd-4ed3-b351-2832d4ceb4bf/lecce_ug_fb_banner_1.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Lecce</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>The goal of the Lecce Ableton User Group is to create a virtual and real group of people who love music production. We are a local support group for Ableton Live, holding a series of events and meetings with experts in the music sector and teachers of music production. We aim to facilitate the exchange of ideas and collaborations between musicians in Lecce</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Andrea Fiorito\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/lecceabletonusergroup/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"87\" ng-show=\"items[87]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/leipzig.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Leipzig</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>The Ableton User Group Leipzig is for everyone producing their own music in the Leipzig area. All levels, styles and formats are welcome.&nbsp;We meet regularly at IfZ (Institut f&uuml;r Zukunft, An den Tierkliniken 38-40). In meetings we have access to the club soundsystem&nbsp;to rehearse projects and sets for mastering, practice or jamming. Also we encourage presentations and workshops from anybody who wants to share their experience.&nbsp;We coordinate meetings via our Instagram Account and Telegram.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Konstantin Hilger\n                \n              </p><p>\n                \n                  Manuel Schmieder\n                \n              </p><p>\n                \n                  Gregor Kachel\n                \n              </p><p>\n                \n                  Dana Ostertag\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/aug_lpz/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Instagram</a></p><p><a href=\"t.me/auglpz\" class=\"has-arrow\">Telegram</a></p><p><a href=\"mailto:abletonusergroupleipzig@gmail.com\" class=\"has-arrow\">abletonusergroupleipzig@gmail.com</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"64\" ng-show=\"items[64]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/community/lille2.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Lille</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Le groupe des geek et des musiciens : les abletonistes (qui jouent du Live ou du Push) et tous les autres&hellip;</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/alexandre-cramoisy-aka-alb/\">Alexandre Cramoisy</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/474947276000767\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"163\" ng-show=\"items[163]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/lima_ug.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">LimaManta</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Grupo creado para compartir informaci&oacute;n, tips, trucos, ideas y experiencias musicales y extra musicales teniendo como base y pretexto el programa Ableton Live y como escenario Lima Per&uacute;.</p><p>Planeamos hacer reuniones peri&oacute;dicas para intercambiar y explorar t&eacute;cnicas y performances, adem&aacute;s de pasarla bien siempre con m&uacute;sica.</p><p>Productores, compositores, m&uacute;sicos, bandas, DJ&#39;s, profesores, artistas visuales de todos los g&eacute;neros y niveles son bienvenidos.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"mailto:ankalli@gmail.com\">Ernesto Peréz</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/abletonusergrouplimamanta/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"256\" ng-show=\"items[256]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/la_ug_fb_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Los Angeles</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Ableton Live Los Angeles is a place to share your Ideas, Events, Workshops, Tutorials, Videos&nbsp;and everything that has to do with Ableton Live.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/yeuda-ben-atar/\">Yeuda Ben-Atar</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/los-angeles-ableton-user-group/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Meetup.com</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/AbletonLiveLA/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"65\" ng-show=\"items[65]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/lyon_ug_fb_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Lyon</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Partager cette passion de la musique &eacute;lectronique sur live parler de votre exp&eacute;rience utilisateur de tout niveaux.<br />\r\nFaites profiter &agrave; la communaut&eacute; lyonnaise et pas seulement. La fa&ccedil;on dont vous utiliser live comment vous ressentez la musique avec Ableton Live.<br />\r\nPr&eacute;senter vos id&eacute;es vos points de vues. Que sera la musique &eacute;lectronique Lyonnaise de demain gr&acirc;ce &agrave; vos recherches sonores.<br />\r\nFaites nous d&eacute;couvrir vos compostions.<br />\r\nbien venue &agrave; toutes &agrave; tous.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/flore-morfin/\">Flore Morfin</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/839843869436151/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"186\" ng-show=\"items[186]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/30/09/30098769-a8f0-4481-830c-69e94b40822e/madrid_ug_fb_banner_1.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Madrid</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Grupo de usuarios Madrile&ntilde;os del software Ableton LIve.</p><p>Este grupo est&aacute; destinado al intercambio de ideas, usos y t&eacute;cnicas de Ableton Live en cualquiera de sus versiones.</p><p>Tus preguntas y soluciones, ser&aacute;n bienvenidas.&nbsp;</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  César Berti\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/436099926475884/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"221\" ng-show=\"items[221]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/22/43/22430349-18a2-4be0-9af0-408628b0459f/manchester_ug_fb_banner_4.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Manchester</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>We host free workshops and events around Manchester and are eager for all producers, musicians or music lovers to come along and chat about music in every way. Whether you are a beginner or a professional, you are always welcome to come and join in and bring your interests to the group and share in its growing popularity.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Dave Fletcher\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p>\n                \n                  djfotn@gmail.com\n                \n              </p><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/297202177084377/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"88\" ng-show=\"items[88]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/5-white_text_export_file.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Mannheim</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p dir=\"ltr\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-7999f146-7fff-8543-b165-ad7fa98e31af\">Beyond lending the famous second pair of ears to you and your music, the Ableton User Group Mannheim offers casual meetings on the following topics:</b></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\"><p dir=\"ltr\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-7999f146-7fff-8543-b165-ad7fa98e31af\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Editing tips and tricks</b></p></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-7999f146-7fff-8543-b165-ad7fa98e31af\">&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Performing on stage</b></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-7999f146-7fff-8543-b165-ad7fa98e31af\">&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Improvisation techniques</b></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-7999f146-7fff-8543-b165-ad7fa98e31af\">&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Field recording and sampling</b></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-7999f146-7fff-8543-b165-ad7fa98e31af\">&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Sound synthesis</b></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-7999f146-7fff-8543-b165-ad7fa98e31af\">&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Scoring for film</b></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-7999f146-7fff-8543-b165-ad7fa98e31af\">&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Data sonification</b></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-7999f146-7fff-8543-b165-ad7fa98e31af\">&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &hellip;and more</b></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-7999f146-7fff-8543-b165-ad7fa98e31af\">We support each other from taking one&rsquo;s first steps with music software to elaborate compository techniques. Or you simply present a tool that you&rsquo;re passionate about. Whether you want to record quarter note scales with your oud, create a canon in Excel oder produce gritty techno &mdash; we love to listen, experiment and think. If it all turns into a concert, so be it. We prefer to meet on-location but we&rsquo;re also curious to explore online formats.</b></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-7999f146-7fff-8543-b165-ad7fa98e31af\">&nbsp;In order to communicate, we use the safe messenger Threema. If you&rsquo;re up for a visit, please contact&nbsp;</b><a href=\"mailto:augma@posteo.de\" target=\"_blank\">augma@posteo.de</a>&nbsp;first.</p><p dir=\"ltr\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-7999f146-7fff-8543-b165-ad7fa98e31af\">&nbsp;Needless to say, participating in our meetings is free of charge.</b></p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Kathrin Grenzdörffer\n                \n              </p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"116\" ng-show=\"items[116]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/mantova_ug_fb_banner2.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Mantova</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>A local Ableton-based community for music production and multimedia programming.</p><p>A place where people in our city can meet to share tips, experiences and techniques.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Andrea Spontoni\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p>\n                \n                  andreaspontoni@gmail.com\n                \n              </p><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/mantovaabletonusergroup\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"68\" ng-show=\"items[68]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/screenshot_2023-08-02_at_144646.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Marseille</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Bienvenue sur le groupe d&#39;utilisateur Ableton Live de Marseille&nbsp;initi&eacute; par Julien Bayle, Ableton Certified Trainer marseillais.</p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ableton.com/en/certified-training/julien-bayle/#?item_type=all\">Julien Bayle</a></p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/marseille.ableton.user.group/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"7\" ng-show=\"items[7]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/user-groups/augm_banner.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Melbourne Australia</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p><b data-stringify-type=\"bold\"><i data-stringify-type=\"italic\">Melbourne&rsquo;s Ableton Live Users Group is a community of music makers of all skill levels drawn together by their interest in learning and sharing creative processes available to them using Ableton&rsquo;s products.</i></b></p><p><b data-stringify-type=\"bold\"><i data-stringify-type=\"italic\">Holding free bi-monthly meet-ups right in the heart of Melbourne, all attendees are encouraged to share their music on a PA system, seek technical feedback, and learn from other like-minded music makers, and special guest speakers.</i></b></p></p><h3>Organizers:</h3><p>\n                \n                  Ryan Powderly\n                \n              </p><h3>Links:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AbletonUserGroupMelbourne\" class=\"has-arrow\">Facebook</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Ableton-User-Group-Melbourne/\" class=\"has-arrow\">Meetup</a></p><p><a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/4umrSEbbXv\" class=\"has-arrow\">Discord</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"146\" ng-show=\"items[146]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/77/3c/773c8e75-f2a0-4ad9-a096-b002fab4f586/25550059_1616548485055028_8265492444287255039_n.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\">Mexico City</h2><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p><p>Grupo oficial de usuarios de Ableton Live en M&eacute;xico. Somos una comunidad, nos reunimos peri&oacute;dicamente para conocernos aprender, compartir y crear.</p></p><h3>Or', 'off');
