class=\"filters__localization__dropdown icon-arrow\"><select ng-model=\"single_selected_by_category[\'language\']\" ng-change=\"single_selected_by_category_updated(\'language\')\" ng-options=\"tag as trans(tag) for tag in tags[\'language\'] | orderBy:trans | filter:tag_is_visible(\'language\')\"><option value=\"\">All languages</option></select></div></div><header class=\"filters__header\"><div class=\"filters__header__title\" trainer-title=\"trainer-title\"></div><div class=\"filters__header__reset-filters\" ng-click=\"clear_filtering()\" ng-show=\"is_filtering_applied()\">Mostrar todo</div></header></div><div class=\"four-up with-padding with-equal-height\"><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"695\" ng-show=\"items[695]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/1500-sound-academy/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/unsorted-uploads/1500_sa_logo_clear_600600.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/1500-sound-academy/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">1500 Sound Academy</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Inglewood CA United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>We solely focus on the development of the modern-day creative through innovative curriculum, elite industry mentorships, and musical partnerships to prepare future artists with nontraditional skill sets for success. 1500 Sound Academy offers a certificate for the Music & Industry Fundamentals Program available On-Campus or Live Online and a digital badge for On-Demand Online Courses designed to develop skills to a professional level in a short amount of time.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"592\" ng-show=\"items[592]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/343-labs/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/e6/03/e60364b6-e4e2-4ae6-8cec-b84a92aebd48/343_labs_logo_square_black_-_max_from_343_labs.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/343-labs/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">343 Labs</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>New York City NY United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>343 Labs is NYC’s fastest growing music production and performance community with free weekly masterclasses, networking events, performance opportunities, and a broad offering of music production courses. With some of NYC’s most accomplished producers on its teaching roster, of which four are Ableton Certified Trainers, students can expect an exceptional educational experience, both in NYC, Berlin, and online.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"630\" ng-show=\"items[630]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/343-labs-berlin/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/d1/b9/d1b9dead-be4c-42b7-94b0-e61de4a7fc53/343_labs_logo_square_black_-_max_wild_1.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/343-labs-berlin/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">343 Labs</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Berlin Germany</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>343 Labs started as a music production school and community in New York City in 2018, and soon grew into a leader for electronic music education. In July 2020, 343 Labs opened its second location at the iconic Riverside Studios in Berlin, making it the only school with locations in both electronic music capitals, New York and Berlin. With some of the world’s most accomplished producers on its teaching roster, of which three are Ableton Certified Trainers, students can expect an exceptional educational experience, in Berlin, NYC and online.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"77\" ng-show=\"items[77]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/40eme-rugissant/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/certified-trainers-training-centers/thumbnail_logofinal.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/40eme-rugissant/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">40ème Rugissant</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Paris France</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Located in the 11th arrondissement of Paris, 40ème Rugissant is a production and post-production structure for documentaries, film music and training in music production techniques. We have trained artists and band members such as Shaka Ponk, Téléphone, Orelsan, Birdy Nam Nam, MC Solar, M83, Zenzile, Katerine, Agar Agar... We also work with the biggest French channels and radios and are proud to work in partnership with Ableton.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"128\" ng-show=\"items[128]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/4cmp/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/certified-trainers-training-centers/4cmp_actc.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/4cmp/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">4CMP</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Milan Italy</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>4CMP Academy (‘For Creative Music Producers’) is a computer music school and production and recording studio located in the center of Milan. The academy offers in-depth courses in Ableton Live, mixing and post-production, and a Higher National Diploma and Bachelor of Arts in Production.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"618\" ng-show=\"items[618]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/aaron-holstein/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/37/d6/37d6beae-9a02-4666-a4c5-f78d3c2df6d3/aaron_holstein.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/aaron-holstein/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Aaron Holstein</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Boulder CO United States</li><li>Denver CO United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Aaron Holstein is a multi-instrumentalist, music and video producer, and Ableton Live instructor\r\nbased in Colorado, USA. He currently releases and performs music as VibeSquaD, BackPact,\r\nAaron Holstein and occasionally with the band Zilla.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"257\" ng-show=\"items[257]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/aaron-zilch/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/2013/04/30/ct_us_aaron_zilch.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/aaron-zilch/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Aaron Zilch</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Los Angeles CA United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Aaron Zilch has been making electronic music for over 18 years. As a teen, his bedroom was a jungle of wires connecting a modular menagerie of hardware drum machines, samplers, and early digital audio workstations. As keyboardist/programmer/sound designer for American Head Charge he was signed to American Recordings. </p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"258\" ng-show=\"items[258]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/abid-hussain/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/2014/01/08/ct_us_abid-hussain_1.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/abid-hussain/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Abid Hussain</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>New Orleans LA United States</li><li>Dallas TX United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Abid Hussain is an electronic and alternative rock producer with more than 25 years of experience. Working as Nebulae, Pellicle, Chlorophyll and Kundalini Shock Attack, he has produced more than 14 self-produced albums, in addition to more than 25 remixes for artists all over the world.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"129\" ng-show=\"items[129]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/absonant/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/07/43/0743f4f1-050d-4955-ac80-afa2e21f38f3/absonant.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/absonant/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Absonant</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Rome Italy</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Absonant is a training center for those wishing to learn audiovisual and multimedia production. Its main objective is to provide students with the skills and capacities they need to become professionals and meet the market demand. </p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"259\" ng-show=\"items[259]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/adam-fangsrud/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/public/2011/11/28/ct_us_adam-fangsrud.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/adam-fangsrud/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Adam Fangsrud</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Missoula MT United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Adam Fangsrud is a producer, engineer and sound artist who has been an Ableton Certified Trainer since 2011.  He is the owner and head engineer at Red Sun Mastering and plays in the electropop duo Flatliner, as well as producing solo techno as Kro.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"11\" ng-show=\"items[11]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/adam-maggs/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/public/2011/09/29/ct_aus_adam-maggs.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/adam-maggs/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Adam Maggs</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Sydney NSW Australia</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Adam Maggs is a producer, DJ, member of the live club act StickFigures and an experienced Ableton Live trainer.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"610\" ng-show=\"items[610]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/adam-partridge/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/5a/e7/5ae75050-da6a-4ed6-911f-95fdc40fc595/adam_partridge.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/adam-partridge/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Adam Partridge</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Woodstock NY United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Adam Partridge aka ‘Atropolis’, has been producing, performing and mixing with Ableton Live for over 10 years.  With releases on various international labels, licensed commercials and scored art installations featured in the Queens Museum and The Shed, Atropolis has also taught Ableton Live for eight years, with extensive experience teaching novice to professional artists.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"465\" ng-show=\"items[465]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/aditya-balani/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/4a/3a/4a3af75c-64ae-4899-91d1-cefa032162dd/aditya_balani.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/aditya-balani/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Aditya Balani</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>New Delhi India</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Aditya Balani is a multi-faceted guitarist, singer-songwriter, music producer and educator from New Delhi, India. A professional musician since 2001 his work has transcended stylistic and international borders.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"260\" ng-show=\"items[260]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/adriano-clemente/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/c8/59/c8590ae9-9ac9-4a7d-8d17-68770964f9ab/adriano_clemente.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/adriano-clemente/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Adriano Clemente</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>New York City NY United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Adriano Clemente has been playing piano since 1990. His first approach to electronic music production was in 1996, when he bought his first analog synthesizer. After several years making computer music and using hardware such as samplers, synths and drum machines, he discovered Ableton Live in 2005, and this completely changed his approach to music production and live performance.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"221\" ng-show=\"items[221]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/adrian-pickard/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/certified-trainers-training-centers/adrian_pickard.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/adrian-pickard/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Adrian Pickard</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Brighton United Kingdom</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Adrian Pickard is one of the first Ableton Certified Trainers worldwide, specializing in music production and live performance techniques with Live.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"99\" ng-show=\"items[99]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/akademia-dzwieku/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/4c/8e/4c8e871b-1cc9-4988-9085-7fc277d4482b/akademia-dzwieku.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/akademia-dzwieku/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Akademia Dzwieku</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Warsaw Poland</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Akademia Dźwięku is one of the biggest music production schools in Poland. Founded in 2008, it’s a pioneer of pro-audio education in the country and offers a wide array of courses, from dedicated Live workshops to live performance, sound design and mixing & mastering.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"667\" ng-show=\"items[667]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/akrti/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/certified-trainers/akrti.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/akrti/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Akrti</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Bangalore India</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Akrti is a singer, and a multi-disciplinary artist from Bangalore, India. Using voice as her primary instrument, she explores the realm of sound across various medium of expression. Her sound reverberates her deep interest in the being and the earthly.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"481\" ng-show=\"items[481]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/alberto-chapa/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/nicht-sortierte-uploads/alberto_chapa.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/alberto-chapa/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Alberto Chapa</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Austin TX United States</li><li>Nuevo Laredo Mexico</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>From solving playback emergencies on festival stages and network TV shows to teaching Ableton Live in a dentist’s office, and in hundreds of people’s bedroom studios; Alberto Chapa is a Certified trainer that is ready for anything!</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"139\" ng-show=\"items[139]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/alessandro-lestino/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/1c/a8/1ca865bf-0183-4dcd-8691-b77534c4d938/alessandro_lestino.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/alessandro-lestino/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Alessandro Lestino</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Torino Italy</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Alessandro Lestino began working as a DJ at the end of the 80\'s, playing in several Italian clubs. During those years his style, inspired originally by rock and R&B, began shifting toward electronic music. In 2003, he set up MusicLab, a recording studio used by many Italian and international artists with very different musical roots.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"140\" ng-show=\"items[140]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/alessandro-rorato/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/4f/56/4f56e39c-dc7a-4210-958e-3583049c7c8c/alessandro_rorato.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/alessandro-rorato/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Alessandro Rorato</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Motta di Livenza (Tv) Italy</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Alessandro has been playing music since 1992. In 1996 he moved from drums to laptop, kicking off his production career. From early on he played electronic music, first exploring drum\'n\'bass, then shifting toward more downtempo styles. In 2001, he was awarded the first prize at the national Coop for Music competition.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"434\" ng-show=\"items[434]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/alexandre-cramoisy-aka-alb/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/c6/ca/c6ca5680-5495-4103-b89c-b3945df7ec92/alexandre_cramoisy.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/alexandre-cramoisy-aka-alb/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Alexandre Cramoisy aka aLb</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Lille France</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>D’abord comédien, c’est aux Beaux-Arts qu’il s’initie à l’audio-numérique avant de devenir auteur-compositeur et interprète (finger-drum, chant, scratch). Son parcours atypique et sa pluridisciplinarité lui permettent de composer aussi bien pour l’art contemporain que pour le spectacle vivant ou les musiques actuelles (hip-hop, électro).</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"113\" ng-show=\"items[113]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/ambrus-deak-aka-amb/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/public/2012/07/25/ct_hu-ambrus-deak.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/ambrus-deak-aka-amb/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Ambrus Deak aka AMB</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Los Angeles CA United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Seasoned music producer. 120+ commercial releases. Winner of iMapp — one of the world’s largest video mapping competitions. 2nd place at The International Breakbeat Awards. Multiple UK Glitch Hop Award nominee. Toured the world. Shared the stage with The Chemical Brothers, Glitch Mob, Tipper.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"125\" ng-show=\"items[125]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/amit-segall/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/certified-trainers-training-centers/amit_segall.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/amit-segall/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Amit Segall</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Tel Aviv Israel</li><li>London United Kingdom</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>As a multidisciplinary artist and musician, Amit loves sharing his knowledge and experiences, both online and face to face, covering a vast variety of expertise of all sorts.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"567\" ng-show=\"items[567]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/anatoly-ice/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/dc/33/dc330bf0-af06-4939-8365-f32d7ebdbda5/anatoly_khachaturov.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/anatoly-ice/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Anatoly Ice</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Moscow Russia</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Анатолий Айс – известный столичный фанкофил и настоящий человек-оркестр: композитор, музыкант, DJ, продюсер, преподаватель, промоутер, радиоведущий с опытом работы в музыкальной индустрии более 25 лет. Организатор и идейный вдохновитель культовых вечеринок «Функции фанка», а также одноименного радио шоу, основным компонентом которых является его знаменитая фонотека.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"187\" ng-show=\"items[187]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/andrei-abramov/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/certified-trainers-training-centers/andrei_abramov_GsknTt6.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/andrei-abramov/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Andrei Abramov</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Moscow Russia</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Andrei Abramov (aka Android) is a professional DJ, producer and teacher with over 25 years of experience.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"185\" ng-show=\"items[185]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/andrei-constantinescu/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/e1/75/e1759720-4c36-493d-8deb-99c17d1e84dc/andrei_constantinescu.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/andrei-constantinescu/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Andrei Constantinescu</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Bucharest Romania</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Andrei “MoShu” Constantinescu started working in the music industry in 1996 and has been involved in many of its fields - from live sound recording and producing, to field recording and post-production for TV and film, as well as sound design for the performing arts.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"595\" ng-show=\"items[595]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/andre-salata/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/20/34/2034bf92-bfcf-4477-ba24-43c888e460a4/andre_salata_-_ct_press_shot.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/andre-salata/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Andre Salata</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>São Paulo Brazil</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Um apaixonado pelo mundo Ableton, Andre demonstra de forma simples e objetiva como o Live e a Push são extensões de sua mente no processo de produção musical, transformando sentimentos em música de maneira descomplicada.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"482\" ng-show=\"items[482]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/andres-power-k-outcode/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/certified-trainers/andres_power.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/andres-power-k-outcode/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Andres Power a.k.a OUTCODE</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Bogotá Colombia</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Andrés Power is a DJ and producer born in Bogotá, Colombia, whose love for music began at the age of 13. With more than 25 years of experience in the electronic music scene, and after exploring different DJ setups and music production tools, he settled on Live as his main creative tool, both in the studio and on stage.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"499\" ng-show=\"items[499]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/anna-lakatos/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/nicht-sortierte-uploads/anna_lakatos.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/anna-lakatos/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Anna Lakatos</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>London United Kingdom</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Anna Lakatos (aka ANNA DISCLAIM) is a London-based electronic musician, singer, trained audio engineer and educator.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"690\" ng-show=\"items[690]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/ansr/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/certified-trainers/hanjin_jung.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/ansr/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">ANSR</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Seoul South Korea</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Techno Live Set 아티스트 & 프로듀서. ANSR은 공연에서 Ableton Live와 함께 Modular Synth 같은 여러 장비를 사용한다. 그는 Ableton Live가 단순한 DAW가 아니며 무한한 가능성을 함께 제공한다고 생각한다. 2014년 부터 Ableton Live와 Push를 사용하기 시작했으며, 이후 다양한 베뉴와 이벤트에서 Live Set 공연을 해오고 있다.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"568\" ng-show=\"items[568]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/anton-anru/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/5e/02/5e02645e-62c8-4ed9-91ce-3b874ee86bff/anton_rukavishnikov.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/anton-anru/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Anton Anru</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Moscow Russia</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Anton Anru – московский продюсер, саунд-дизайнер, микс-инженер и преподаватель по музыкальному продакшну. В творчестве и обучении охватывает жанры: pop/song, modern jazz, indie, instrumental, electronica, ambient, house, breakbeat. В своей работе Антон делает особый упор на уникальности звучания благодаря детальной проработке аранжировки и саунд-дизайна. Его цель найти и раскрыть индивидуальность в каждом ученике.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"100\" ng-show=\"items[100]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/antonio-kriznic/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/certified-trainers-training-centers/antonio_kriznic.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/antonio-kriznic/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Antonio Križnič</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Velenje Slovenia</li><li>Ljubljana Slovenia</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Antonio Križnič is an electronic music composer, performer and educator. He has been involved in computer music since the late nineties and has experimented with sound in various forms. After discovering Live in 2003, he began using it to expand his techno live performances and studio productions. Artistically, Antonio is known as Tonske, and he is a co-founder of electronic music organization and newly established techno label, Cogo.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"262\" ng-show=\"items[262]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/antonio-sage/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/nicht-sortierte-uploads/antonio_sage.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/antonio-sage/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Antonio Sage</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Las Vegas NV United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Antonio Sage is a Multi-Instrumentalist /Vocalist and Composer. He has written, performed and produced a vast catalog for clients such as Warner Chappell Production Music, Revolution, Groove Addicts, and Emergency Production Music. His compositions are featured in television programs and networks such as Judge Judy, Dr. Oz Show, The Morning Show, House Hunters International, Primer Impacto, Networks include; HBO, Fox, TNT, Univision, and MTV2.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"78\" ng-show=\"items[78]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/apaxx-designs/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/2013/03/04/actc_fr_apaxx.jpeg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/apaxx-designs/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">APAXX DESIGNS</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Paris France</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Apaxxdesigns is a high-profile facility in Paris, France. Run by Jean-Louis Hennequin, a well-known musician, producer, composer, and Apple Certified Logic Master Trainer, Apaxxdesigns is aimed at providing experienced audio users that extra bit that only real-world experience can provide. </p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"1\" ng-show=\"items[1]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/arjaus/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/fa/cc/faccfe0b-4b78-4dce-821b-335558e9101c/arjaus_school.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/arjaus/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Arjaus</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Buenos Aires Argentina</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>At Arjaus you’ll find a sense of family and community, while constantly developing your skills. You’ll be in a comfortable place where the institution is always by your side, helping you to grow on the musical spectrum that you like​, as a human and as a team member.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"454\" ng-show=\"items[454]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/aryaman-agarwal/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/a9/3e/a93ec43e-9792-4619-8a55-7eb09aab3144/ableton_trainer_profile_600600.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/aryaman-agarwal/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Aryaman Agarwal</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>New Delhi India</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Aryaman Agarwal is a music producer and educator from New Delhi, India.\r\nHe is primarily an electronic musician and began producing his own music using Live in 2012. After discovering the intricacies of the software, he started experimenting with different techniques of synthesis and sound design to create different genres of music.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"453\" ng-show=\"items[453]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/ashrith-baburao/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/66/2c/662c98ba-55d4-4368-85a2-5b76fe15adc8/ashrith_baburao.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/ashrith-baburao/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Ashrith Baburao</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Bangalore India</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Ashrith Baburao is the co-founder of Beatworx, one of India’s most acclaimed electronic music schools. Since 2011, he’s been producing and performing music with his brother as Audio Units, a nationally recognized duo. Ashrith’s tryst with computers began in 1994, when he was three years old, and he has been wonderstruck by technology ever since. A high school graduate on paper, he went on to prove that formal education isn\'t everything.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"332\" ng-show=\"items[332]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/askvideocom-macprovideocom/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/5c/bd/5cbdc794-0e49-4eff-9f1a-9c63d0ffde56/askvideo_macprovideo.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/askvideocom-macprovideocom/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">AskVideo.com / macProVideo.com</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>NonLinear Educating’s macProVideo.com course library has over 50 hours of Ableton Live and Push courses led by world class DJs, performers and Certified Trainers. Get a Library Pass subscription which gives you unlimited access to macProVideo.com and their ask.video site as well! Two great sites. Same great courses.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"131\" ng-show=\"items[131]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/audio-engine-music-x/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/04/71/047186c6-2d30-40f1-8f5f-51e5f93d3f72/audio_engine_music.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/audio-engine-music-x/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Audio Engine Music</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Cento Italy</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Audio Engine Music is one of the most prestigious certified training centers in Italy. Through the years it has become an influential and popular center for students seeking Apple, Adobe, PearsonVUE, Avid and Ableton certified training.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"186\" ng-show=\"items[186]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/audioschool/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/certified-trainers-training-centers/audioschool.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/audioschool/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Audioschool</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Moscow Russia</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Audioschool offers world-class Ableton Live training from anywhere in the world. Courses in Ableton Live include production, DJing, composition and arrangements, sound design, mixing, mastering, live performance and more. Studio-based and online courses teach students how to create release-ready tracks from scratch, in any genre.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"42\" ng-show=\"items[42]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/beat-drop/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/67/c9/67c9bb62-4afb-423c-82f7-90702276574d/beat_drop.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/beat-drop/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Beat Drop</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Calgary AB Canada</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Beat Drop is an online electronic music production and DJ school based in Calgary, Alberta. We are a community of musicians, DJs and producers of all genres who enjoy producing, creating and performing music. We offer online courses and mentorship in Ableton Live.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"675\" ng-show=\"items[675]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/beat-kitchen/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/unsorted-uploads/beatkitchenlogo_black_600x600.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/beat-kitchen/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Beat Kitchen</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>New York City NY United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Beat Kitchen is the soup-to-nuts music production school for creatives. We are artist-instructors teaching music production, live, in small classes. We began with a vision: to provide a place for creatives to play with their food.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"544\" ng-show=\"items[544]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/belle-murphy/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/certified-trainers/belle_murphy.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/belle-murphy/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Belle Murphy</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Melbourne VIC Australia</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Belle Murphy is a Melbourne, Australia based electronic music-maker, educator and community facilitator. Specialising in the blend of creative approach and technical know-how, Belle is right at home in the world of electronic production, sharing the science behind the systems and developing unique solutions for the stage.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"505\" ng-show=\"items[505]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/ben-ang/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/ba/4e/ba4ea446-11f6-405a-921a-89bd182500a3/ben-music-profile1-600600.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/ben-ang/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Ben Ang</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Singapore Singapore</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Ben Ang, Electronic Music instructor in Singapore, Principal Tutor of NUS Electronic Music Lab, Instructor at Pop Studio Academy, Producer of synthpop / remix duo Cosmic Armchair, teaches electronic music production and performance with Ableton Live, Ableton Push, and Max for Live.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"323\" ng-show=\"items[323]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/ben-casey/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/a8/dd/a8dd85ed-e166-46b0-919b-1b62f3aeca5c/ct_us_ben-casey.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/ben-casey/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Ben Casey</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>New York City NY United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Ben Casey is a Brooklyn-based electronic musician, Ableton Certified Trainer, and overall music tech nerd. When he’s not surrounded by wires and drum machines or tinkering with Max for Live, Ben teaches Ableton Live to musicians across all genres, from avant-garde to zydeco.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"322\" ng-show=\"items[322]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/ben-hovey/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/2014/10/06/ct_us_ben-hovey.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/ben-hovey/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Ben Hovey</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Asheville NC United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Trumpet/keyboard player, synthesist, and sonic scientist Ben Hovey, aka HoveyKraft, blends his artistry as an accomplished traditional musician with a deep knowledge of music technology, into a truly rare talent.  His musical roots began at age 5 in 1982 with piano. </p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"91\" ng-show=\"items[91]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/ben-vedren/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/78/a5/78a58fd9-e28a-4968-9375-a2dad61d2e01/benoit_vedrenne.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/ben-vedren/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Ben Vedren</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Paris France</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Ben is a french electronic artist, DJ, and Ableton Certified Trainer. For many years now, he has been sharing his knowledge and musical approach throughout groups trainings, one to one sessions and masterclasses.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"326\" ng-show=\"items[326]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/berklee-online/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/26/ea/26ea304f-8442-439d-817e-a1ee3544e5eb/berklee_online.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/berklee-online/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Berklee Online</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Advance your Ableton Live skills with Berklee Online, the award-winning online school of Berklee College of Music. Study Berklee\'s renowned music production techniques directly from our faculty members, inside highly interactive online classrooms alongside like-minded musicians and industry professionals.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"475\" ng-show=\"items[475]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/bimm-london/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/unsorted-uploads/bimm-music_institute_black600600_VtuRe90.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/bimm-london/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">BIMM London</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>London United Kingdom</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Part of BIMM University, BIMM Music Institute London is an Ableton Certified Training Centre. They open the doors to the music industry, encouraging creative freedom, providing real-world industry experiences and building a community across our colleges in the UK, Ireland and Germany.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"696\" ng-show=\"items[696]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/bimm-university-berlin/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/unsorted-uploads/bimm_university_berlin_logo_black_sept23.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/bimm-university-berlin/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">BIMM University Berlin</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Berlin Germany</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>At BIMM University, we provide an extensive range of courses in modern music, performing arts, filmmaking, and creative technology to over 8,000 students across 14 schools in the UK, Ireland, and Germany. We have a long-standing commitment to providing the highest quality in creative industries education, allowing students to maximise their career potential.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"548\" ng-show=\"items[548]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/box-hill-institute/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/13/ef/13efe4d2-79a0-499a-aa30-5dfb2aa958fa/box_hill_600600.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/box-hill-institute/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Box Hill Institute</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Melbourne VIC Australia</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Box Hill Institute have been the leaders in contemporary music education for the last 35 years. With the best facilities in the southern hemisphere for music education and two certified Ableton Live trainers on staff, Box Hill offers quality training in Ableton Live from short course through to Certificates, Diplomas and degrees.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"123\" ng-show=\"items[123]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/bpm-college/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/71/e9/71e99b2a-dd8d-4a76-964e-5b3183e03f5d/bpm_college_ltd.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/bpm-college/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">BPM College</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Tel Aviv Israel</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>BPM College is a leading music and sound school in Israel and was established in 2003 by Idan Huna & Yariv Etzion. Their goal is to give the best training for producers, musicians & sound engineers and take in over 700 students a year.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"263\" ng-show=\"items[263]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/brandon-murphy/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/unsorted-uploads/new_profile600px.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/brandon-murphy/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Brandon Murphy</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Detroit MI United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Brandon is a multi-disciplinary audio artist, musician, engineer and educator, primarily based in Detroit, MI.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"114\" ng-show=\"items[114]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/bray-institute-of-further-education/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/f4/5b/f45b06af-4753-4834-be8c-a47e6364c6fa/bray_institute_of_further_education.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/bray-institute-of-further-education/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">bray institute of further education</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Bray Ireland</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>At the Bray Institute of Further Education (BIFE), we give students the practical skills needed to secure work in the industry. </p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"265\" ng-show=\"items[265]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/brian-funk/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/2013/12/03/ct_us_brian_funk.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/brian-funk/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Brian Funk</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Long Island NY United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Brian Funk is a songwriter, producer, and educator from New York.  Brian hosts The Music Production Podcast and teaches music production for Berklee Online. Sounds from Brian’s Ableton Live Packs are used by producers all over the world.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"266\" ng-show=\"items[266]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/brian-jackson/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/certified-trainers/brian_jackson.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/brian-jackson/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Brian Jackson</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>New York City NY United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Brian M. Jackson is a music producer, electronic musician, audio engineer, educator, consultant, and author of The Music Producer\'s Survival Guide: Chaos, Creativity, and Career in Independent and Electronic Music (Sound on Sound Presents…). Brian is an expert instructor with more than 20 years of teaching experience, and is as comfortable lecturing to large groups as he is providing intimate one-on-one training.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"267\" ng-show=\"items[267]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/brian-markman/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/60/f1/60f19a20-a752-4d81-9a0f-91c0550f3340/brian_markman.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/brian-markman/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Brian Markman</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Los Angeles CA United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Brian Markman is an engineer, producer and club DJ. Starting over 12 years ago playing records at acid jazz clubs and then at raves playing drum and bass, technology pushed his musical interests forward. 2 years ago, Markman came to SAE as an instructor in the Electronic Music Production program teaching Ableton Live. </p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"59\" ng-show=\"items[59]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/brian-smith/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/public/2012/07/25/ct_de_brian-smith.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/brian-smith/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Brian Smith</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Berlin Germany</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Brian Smith’s musical journey began with studying the piano (from age five) and trumpet (from age nine). He received a Bachelor\'s degree in music from the University of California, Santa Cruz, where he began composing at the electronic music studio. In the mid-1980s he co-founded the experimental industrial band Language Lab in San Francisco, then moved to Paris and immersed himself in the contemporary music scene there, working at IRCAM for several months before going on to create sound installations and compositions independently.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"516\" ng-show=\"items[516]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/byungryul-lee/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/29/0e/290e8e10-3fd4-452c-a5b5-9cc8989dc4c4/byungryul_lee.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/byungryul-lee/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Byungryul Lee</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Seoul South Korea</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Byungryul Lee, aka Mute, is an electronic music & RnB producer and sound designer.\r\nHe began his musical career composing electronic music for film, TV and commercials. Byungryul Lee currently writes RnB music and contributes sound design to AUIs (Auditory User Interface) for technology companies such as Samsung.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"566\" ng-show=\"items[566]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/camiel-daamen/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/f2/59/f2591037-dd8c-4bcf-a231-c18b50511c6c/camiel_daamen.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/camiel-daamen/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Camiel Daamen</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Amsterdam Netherlands</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Camiel Daamen is bekend van zijn veelzijdige dj en livesets. Vaak met een goede groove met veel percussieve elementen tussendoor. Zijn sound is moeilijk in een hokje te plaatsen omdat hij techno bangers net zo makkelijk maakt als ambient soundscapes. Droevig of blij, pompend of relaxend het past allemaal in zijn veelzijdige sound. Het past ook goed bij zijn Energieke, emotionele en altijd lachende persoonlijkheid.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"342\" ng-show=\"items[342]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/carles-reixach/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/f3/d9/f3d9d116-bfc3-4405-a990-547df8cede0d/carles_reixach.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/carles-reixach/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Carles Reixach</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Girona Spain</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Carles is an electronic music and soundtrack artist, producer, and Dj, as well as being the CEO, and an experienced teacher of Live and Push, at the Eumes Advanced Music & Sound School.\r\n</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"55\" ng-show=\"items[55]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/carlos-polania/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/54/83/5483b018-0fab-4939-b70c-c0634c57deb7/carlos_polonia.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/carlos-polania/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Carlos Polania</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Bogotá Colombia</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Carlos Polania is a Music producer based in Bogota. While in high school, the impact that music and sound had on his life, drove him to begin experimenting with recording sounds and loops on a tape machine.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"335\" ng-show=\"items[335]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/catalyst/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/certified-trainers-training-centers/catalyst.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/catalyst/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Catalyst</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Berlin Germany</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Catalyst is a creative arts and technology learning institute based at the historic Funkhaus in Berlin. It has been providing world-class creative production training in the UK for 20 years, and in Berlin since 2013 under the former brand name of dBs Music Berlin.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"176\" ng-show=\"items[176]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/cenk-unis/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/b9/ae/b9ae4d02-6117-42ab-a74d-8afe22f2d734/cenk_unis.jpeg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/cenk-unis/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Cenk Unis</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Istanbul Turkey</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Cenk Unis is a producer, Dj, member of the visual entertainment collective ShiTv, and an experienced Ableton Live trainer. His journey with music began at a very young age. As a resident DJ he became a professional in 1991.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"194\" ng-show=\"items[194]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/cesar-berti/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/0d/1b/0d1b5213-7be3-4f60-97e3-8f5a20b5c28a/cesar_berti.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/cesar-berti/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Cesar Berti</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Madrid Spain</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Cesar\'s musical career started in the 1990s, when he worked as a DJ. In 2003, he discovered computer music and began his career as a composer and producer.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"467\" ng-show=\"items[467]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/cesma/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/76/27/7627ef8a-6e38-4ab4-bac3-3db395f4efcd/cesma.jpeg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/cesma/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">CESMA</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Lugano Switzerland</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>CESMA is a multi-disciplinary research and teaching facility providing higher education in audio engineering, music and acoustics, certified by eduQua in Switzerland. We offer a wide range of programs, from higher education and federal exams to vocational and short-term courses in music technology and production.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"560\" ng-show=\"items[560]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/champion-sound/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/de/9a/de9a980b-ae34-40f3-9fc4-b0d92bc31e8b/champion_sound_logo_600x600.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/champion-sound/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Champion Sound</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Portland OR United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Champion Sound is a music production and DJ school, offering affordable Ableton Live and DJ courses in Portland, Oregon.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"268\" ng-show=\"items[268]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/charles-noel/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/public/2011/10/05/ct_us_charles-noel.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/charles-noel/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Charles Noel</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>New York City NY United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Charles is resident specialist of electronic music production, DJing and performance at the School of Audio Engineering. With almost twenty years of experience in the electronic music industry, Charles has produced albums for labels in Europe and has toured worldwide...</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"473\" ng-show=\"items[473]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/charly-fariseo/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/eb/8d/eb8d7bdc-45f3-40e9-921f-1a0a3f916441/carlos_mora_charly.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/charly-fariseo/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Charly Fariseo</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>San José Costa Rica</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Charly Fariseo is a multi-instrumentalist, producer, composer and live performer from San José, Costa Rica. He has been an Ableton Certified Trainer since 2014 and specializes in working on audio branding, sound design and post-production for TV, radio and web media. Charly teaches music production and currently performs with his band Rombos.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"177\" ng-show=\"items[177]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/che-van-workum/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/80/e9/80e9d643-0975-4db5-9676-50e6cca01124/che_van_workum_600600.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/che-van-workum/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Ché van Workum</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Rotterdam Netherlands</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Ché van Workum has been a DJ and producer since 2000. After discovering Ableton Live in 2006 (version 5), he decided to become a professional in the music industry. Since 2007, Ché has run the SoundKings music platform and is also responsible for the house and techno sub-label, SKUG, organizing events throughout Rotterdam and the Netherlands.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"525\" ng-show=\"items[525]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/chiara-fella/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/a9/f4/a9f470f0-55df-4a3f-beb2-29d4e579ea63/krezie.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/chiara-fella/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Chiara Fella</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Milan Italy</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Chiara Fella is a teacher, producer and performer based in Milan, Italy. Singing, music and technology are at the center of her life.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"543\" ng-show=\"items[543]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/chris-cox/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/11/79/1179f260-3097-4203-87bc-4200708107df/chris_cox.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/chris-cox/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Chris Cox (Frank Booker)</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Auckland New Zealand</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Chris Cox aka Frank Booker, is a DJ, producer, music consultant, educator and Ableton Live\r\nCertified trainer based in Auckland, New Zealand.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"269\" ng-show=\"items[269]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/chris-dilday/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/public/2012/03/08/ct_us_chris-dilday.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/chris-dilday/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Chris Dilday</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Nashville TN United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Chris Dilday is a musician, producer, DJ and engineer based in Nashville, Tennessee. A drummer since age 10 and a DJ since 16, he has immersed himself in music from an early age.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"392\" ng-show=\"items[392]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/chris-petti/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/66/a3/66a359a8-b59c-427d-89c2-81167d8d6b7c/chris_petti.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/chris-petti/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Chris Petti</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>New York City NY United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Chris is a musician, producer, sound designer, educator, and certified music technology junkie for life…</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"239\" ng-show=\"items[239]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/chris-pratt/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/certified-trainers-training-centers/chris_pratt.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/chris-pratt/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Chris Pratt</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Plymouth United Kingdom</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Chris Pratt has been performing and producing with Ableton Live for almost 20 years. He has a wealth of experience helping learners of ranging ability to develop effective workflows for composition, production and performance using systems centred around Ableton Live.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"270\" ng-show=\"items[270]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/chris-schlyer/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/public/2011/10/05/ct_us_chris-schlyer.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/chris-schlyer/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Chris Schlyer</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Seattle WA United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Chris Schlyer is a musician, performer and sound designer based out of Seattle, WA. He is heavily involved in the video game industry and has worked for companies such as Sony Computer Entertainment of America and Activision Blizzard, using Live as a tool for interactive audio development. </p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"169\" ng-show=\"items[169]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/christian-sanchez-red/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/f8/81/f8813fab-4c15-44f6-b037-2f23d797883f/christian_sanchezjpg__600x600_q85.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/christian-sanchez-red/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Christian Sánchez (RED)</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Merida Yucatan Mexico</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Hailing from southern Mexico, where he’s been involved in underground electronic music for over 10 years, Christian “Red” Sánchez has been instrumental in invigorating the music scene of his home region.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"462\" ng-show=\"items[462]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/christian-schwanz/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/nicht-sortierte-uploads/christian_schwanz.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/christian-schwanz/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Christian Schwanz aka. CEE</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Berlin Germany</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Producing music under the moniker Cee, Christian Schwanz has long been at the global forefront of eclectic, electronic bass music, with projects like Al-Haca and Bass Sekolah.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"446\" ng-show=\"items[446]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/christian-thomas/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/unsorted-uploads/cthomas_headshot.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/christian-thomas/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Christian Thomas</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Nashville TN United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Christian Thomas is a Nashville-based musician, producer, instructor and consultant. He is the owner of Live Stems, a music performance consulting company specializing in audio/MIDI playback solutions with a client roster that includes many of today\'s top artists. Christian has been an Ableton Live user since 2002 and has been actively providing instruction for over two decades.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"619\" ng-show=\"items[619]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/christina-horn/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/3d/31/3d312ed2-b0c0-4541-922e-0ac135f71f60/christina_horn.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/christina-horn/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Christina Horn</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Knoxville TN United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Christina Horn, AKA Hudson K, is a pianist, singer, songwriter, composer and educator who has been integrating Live into her performances since 2009. She has been actively touring and teaching for a decade and is interested in the intersection between art and technology.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"79\" ng-show=\"items[79]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/cifap/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/certified-trainers-training-centers/logoncifap_600600.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/cifap/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Cifap</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Paris France</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>CIFAP is a leading provider of high-quality professional training for workers in the creative industries. Every year over 150 professionals participate in training courses tailored to their specific needs.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"605\" ng-show=\"items[605]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/claire-marie-lim/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/08/84/0884eb11-4841-491b-81ba-23a64934840c/claire_marie_lim.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/claire-marie-lim/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Claire Marie Lim (dolltr!ck)</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>New York City NY United States</li><li>Singapore Singapore</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Claire Marie Lim is a Singapore-born music technologist and educator, also active under her artist project dolltr!ck. She specializes in instruction for live electronic performance, production and programming, and is an advocate of women and Asian representation in music technology.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"572\" ng-show=\"items[572]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/collarts/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/2c/0b/2c0b82ff-fe7c-4f5e-af75-fefdf2fb3961/collarts_logo_-_david_jacob.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/collarts/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Collarts</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Melbourne VIC Australia</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Collarts (Australian College of the Arts Pty Ltd) is a dynamic independent tertiary education college full of passion, individuality and opportunity. Focused on creating real career pathways into the creative sector for students, Collarts delivers industry-based learning coupled with strong personal and professional development.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"195\" ng-show=\"items[195]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/cora-novoa/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/certified-trainers-training-centers/cora_novoa.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/cora-novoa/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Cora Novoa</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Barcelona Spain</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Cora Novoa is a professional producer, DJ, sound technician and freelance music tech tutor from Spain. Trained as a classical musician and a flutist since 1997, Cora is also a sound and IT technician, and holds several Apple certifications.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"271\" ng-show=\"items[271]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/corey-baker/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/be/58/be58538b-5b51-46a3-871b-3b3931d5f1aa/corey_baker.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/corey-baker/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Corey Baker</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Austin TX United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Corey Baker, professionally known as both Kill Paris and Hobbie Sound, is a multi-instrumental producer living in Denver, Colorado.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"443\" ng-show=\"items[443]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/costas-papa/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/47/b6/47b6b3f9-875a-4699-b458-35c8defade99/costas_papa.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/costas-papa/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Costas Papa</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Dubai United Arab Emirates</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Costas is a Dubai based sonic artist, music producer and consultant. He’s an expert educator with more than 10 years of experience and the founder of Granular Academy.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"122\" ng-show=\"items[122]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/createsoundie/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/53/b2/53b2ad41-496c-4a45-adfd-3fed9610b976/createsound.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/createsoundie/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">createsound.ie</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Ireland</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Since 2011, CreateSound has been running courses and workshops, supplying all the latest hardware and Ableton software on site, with regular courses in over 100 locations in Ireland and the UK to date. Now we’ve moved everything online so students can participate in our courses wherever they are, whatever their level.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"485\" ng-show=\"items[485]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/cristian-c-funk-moraga/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/unsorted-uploads/thumbnail_c-funk2023_2179_ed1321.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/cristian-c-funk-moraga/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Cristian “C-Funk” Moraga</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Santiago Chile</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Cristián Moraga is a singer, composer, guitar & keyboard player, producer and one of the most renowned funk artists from Chile. His impressive international career with Los Tetas, beginning in 1995, made him a well-known figure of both funk and hip-hop in Latin America.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"178\" ng-show=\"items[178]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/cristiano-nicolini/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/2e/ff/2effeb64-b984-4c7f-a09c-ce278a149c7d/unknown.png__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/cristiano-nicolini/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Cristiano Nicolini</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>London United Kingdom</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Cristiano Nicolini is a London-based music producer, sound engineer, tech-consultant and Ableton Certified Trainer.  He makes music as Mattokind, BleakHouse and PlastikJoy.  He has worked as a studio engineer and producer for Dubfire, Nicole Moudaber and Deep Dish, as well as various artists from Get Physical, Second State and SCI+TEC labels.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"25\" ng-show=\"items[25]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/damien-goundrie/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/2014/02/13/ct_aus_damien-goundrie.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/damien-goundrie/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Damien Goundrie</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Hobart TAS Australia</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Damien started his career as a DJ in the early nineties and released his first track in ’94. He has worked in a variety of roles within the music industry ever since. A long-standing association with production, radio, and retail makes Damien the perfect mentor for young producers.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"272\" ng-show=\"items[272]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/dan-freeman/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/58/dc/58dc61fa-e3fe-47e8-b303-7ec75332d191/df600600.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/dan-freeman/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Dan Freeman (CØm1x)</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>New York City NY United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Dan FreeMan (CØm1x) is a producer, bassist, and music technologist based in Brooklyn, New York. After graduating from Harvard University, he came to New York to be a session bassist. As a bass player he has performed with such artists as Angelique Kidjo and the B-52’s.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"611\" ng-show=\"items[611]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/dan-giffin/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/7e/83/7e835eb7-0168-4058-aab5-4dbe2e67e6c7/dan_giffin.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/dan-giffin/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Dan Giffin</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Denver CO United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>As a well-experienced producer and performer, Dan Giffin has taught Grammy-winning artists the ins and outs of making music with Live and Push. He currently produces under the artist name Philia, teaches Ableton Live through his website LiveProducersOnline.com and hosts the Ableton Music Producer Podcast.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"344\" ng-show=\"items[344]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/daniel-cantero/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/76/07/76074a43-a8a3-4624-8c7c-bcfed600e368/daniel_cantero.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/daniel-cantero/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Daniel Cantero</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Madrid Spain</li><li>Brighton United Kingdom</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Working as a sonologist, sound designer and music producer and combining these skills with his role as a hardware and software developer, Daniel Cantero is a talented all round audiovisual engineer managing research projects for the Digital Luthier company, which he founded. </p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"142\" ng-show=\"items[142]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/daniele-mattiuzzi/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/11/1a/111a0cfb-33ee-4b0a-a1ee-98f8c73891a0/lele_con_cuffie_300x300_sito_1.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/daniele-mattiuzzi/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Daniele Mattiuzzi</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Torino Italy</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Daniele Mattiuzzi discovered Ableton Live in 2002, and has since become a specialist in music production using this software. His broad musical background and interests led him to attend the SAE Institute in Milan, where he obtained a diploma in Audio Engineering.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"564\" ng-show=\"items[564]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/daniel-kohlmeigner/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/certified-trainers/daniel_kohlmeigner.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/daniel-kohlmeigner/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Daniel Kohlmeigner</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Viena Austria</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>After using Ableton Live for 20 years on stage and in the studio, Daniel now also teaches musicians and develops new study programs. His practical and fun approach has excited hundreds of students from university to public schools and private lessons.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"612\" ng-show=\"items[612]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/danielle-thwaites/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/04/f5/04f5e55d-dcb9-49b4-bc43-60329e159023/danielle_thwaites.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/danielle-thwaites/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Danielle Thwaites</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Los Angeles CA United States</li><li>Dallas TX United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Danielle Thwaites (Daiza) has extensive versatility and expertise as a producer, songwriter, instrumentalist, educator and live show designer. She works to enable people to creatively express themselves with music technology.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"596\" ng-show=\"items[596]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/danilo-bencke/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/36/58/36588c7d-b193-43e1-8cd1-fe3cd6632813/600600danilo_bencke_-_dancko.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/danilo-bencke/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Danilo Bencke</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Curitiba Brazil</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Danilo Bencke é DJ e Produtor no seu projeto de Bass House / G-House \"Dancko\" e atua como professor na mais renomada escola de DJs e Produção Musical do Brasil, a AIMEC. Além disso, trabalha com mixagem & masterização e como jornalista, tendo uma coluna quinzenal na House Mag, considerado a maior revista de música eletrônica da América Latina.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"143\" ng-show=\"items[143]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/danilo-rispoli/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/public/2011/10/05/ct_it_danilo-rispoli.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/danilo-rispoli/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Danilo Rispoli</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Palermo Italy</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Danilo Rispoli is a DJ, producer, sound designer, teacher, festival promoter and label manager. He began producing house and techno in 1989, and eventually Danilo productions reached the top positions of most relevant European and American charts, such as DMC and Billboard. In 2005, Danilo fell in love with Ableton.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"16\" ng-show=\"items[16]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/danny-bonnici/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/96/dc/96dc0eea-0cbe-471f-8036-a4e9f91eeaab/danny_bonnici.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/danny-bonnici/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Danny Bonnici</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Melbourne VIC Australia</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Over the past 14 years Danny Bonnici has been at the forefront of the global dance music scene. Danny’s tracks have featured on labels ranging from Renaissance to Global Underground,YK4, MOB, Vicious Vinyl, and more.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"526\" ng-show=\"items[526]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/dario-tatoli/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/17/5b/175bf11e-7a04-418b-88cb-92ccb2e28a6b/dario_tatoli_-_ableton_ct_photo_5_.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/dario-tatoli/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Dario Tatoli</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Rome Italy</li><li>Bari Italy</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Dario Tatoli is a sound designer, musician and producer. Since 2011, he has taught hundreds of students using Ableton Live. An explorer of sound creation and manipulation, Dario focuses on different musical languages, encouraging students to develop their own musical identity.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"468\" ng-show=\"items[468]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/darren-kramer/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/51/a2/51a21e0e-ba5d-4e52-91e4-231ac6c9344d/darren_kramer.jpeg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/darren-kramer/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Darren Kramer</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Denver CO United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Darren Kramer is an innovative Electric Trombone DJ, XO Professional Brass Artist, and Ableton Certified Trainer, creating live remixes of originals and covers via live looping, effects, Push beat slicing, virtual synths, vocoder and the iPad Lemur app. He’s been a professional musician for over 30 years, working as a full-time freelance trombonist, pianist, composer, producer and educator.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"17\" ng-show=\"items[17]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/dave-dizz1-norris/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/images/certified-trainers/dave_norris.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/dave-dizz1-norris/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">Dave &quot;Dizz1&quot; Norris</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Melbourne VIC Australia</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Dave Norris, widely known as Dizz1, is a Melbourne-based creative luminary who has left an indelible mark on the world of bass music. His journey began as a turntablist, producer, and drummer, where he developed a unique “feel” that transcended scratching, drumming, and programming those signature sideways beats.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"439\" ng-show=\"items[439]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/david-engstrom/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/8e/73/8e73ffea-d0e1-444d-8c40-b9cc3da6118a/david_engstrom.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/david-engstrom/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">David Engström</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Arvika Sweden</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>David Engström is a versatile musician, producer and music teacher, with a passion for synthesizers, electronic music, experimentation and improvisation.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"273\" ng-show=\"items[273]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/david-lopez/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/93/0e/930e3628-d51c-446b-affd-b62f7002526c/david_lopez.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/david-lopez/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">David Lopez</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Atlanta GA United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>David Lopez aka Didactic is an audio production & technology professional with over 15 years of diverse experience as an Audio Engineer, Consultant, Educator, Producer, DJ and Ableton Certified Trainer.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"54\" ng-show=\"items[54]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/david-najera/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/76/34/76349f16-0dc5-4fcf-8d13-4f7d27226867/david_najera.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/david-najera/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">David Najera</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Bogotá Colombia</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>David Najera has been involved in the music world as a Dj and Music Producer for over 10 years. He began using Ableton Live in 2006, and started teaching music production in different environments around the same time.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"cell\" data-item-id=\"620\" ng-show=\"items[620]\"><div class=\"pack-teaser\"><div class=\"pack-teaser__media\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/david-sharma/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\"><img class=\"js-lazyload-image\" src=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/80bA26cPQ1hEJDFjpUKntxfqdmG3ZykO/static/images/placeholder.fc1d63f8f093.gif\" data-original=\"https://cdn-resources.ableton.com/resources/filer_thumbnails/04/88/048834e8-c0d0-4bca-b7d9-c32d66f380e8/dave_sharma.jpg__300x300_q85_crop_subsampling-2_upscale.jpg\"></a></div><h2 class=\"pack-teaser__title\"><a href=\"/es/certified-training/david-sharma/\" preserve-query=\"preserve-query\">David Sharma</a></h2><ul class=\"type-s\"><li>Houston TX United States</li></ul><div class=\"pack-teaser__description\"><div class=\"body-text body-text--small\"><p>Percussionist, producer and educator', 'off');
